review: i bought these glasses for a halloween party and they were pretty darn cooluntil they stopped working  after approximately  hours of use the light went out and never came back on  i immediately thought the batteries died so i replaced them with new ones i had with me but that didnt rectify the problem  i visually inspected the wiring and the neon piping but there was no obvious damage or loose parts  the red light on the battery pack lit up with each press of the button as i toggled through the lighting options solid slow blink fast blink and seeing as though the batteries and battery pack were working i concluded that it was a wiring issue likely stemming from dancingi contacted amazon about the problem whose outstanding customer support issued me a refund upon receipt of my glassesi rated  stars because the glasses were of good quality and were what i expected based on videos and pictures i viewed prior to purchase  one thing i definitely advise is to order the clear lenses if wearing them in a low light setting youll be glad you did

review: i have spd and the pressure on my pelvis was getting unbearable even walking was very painful my dr suggested a belly brace i wanted something that would help me but was hesitant to spend the extra money everyone i tried on in the store was terrible uncomfortable and made my body look awkward the sales clerk suggested layering it over a tank so it wouldnt irritate my skin like im not hot enough alreadyi ordered the upsie belly based on product reviews never having tried it on personally it is exactly what i neededit is comfortable against my skin made from a soft bamboo fabric that actually breathes even in  degree whetherit provides perfect support and has nearly eliminated my very irritating symptoms of spd and even helped with the ligament pain i was having back pain goneit is flattering under even fitted clothes it may be visible but does not contort my shape like the others im not that skinny under regular clothes it can be worn undetectedi found the size to be accurate to my maternity size i have been wearing large maternity clothes and ordered a large belt it fits perfectlyi have not yet used the heatingice packs but i am sure i will soon this is a nice featurebottom line if you are shopping around nothing else compares this truly is worth every penny

review: this is awesome i got the darth maul for my father who is a big star wars fan and he absolutely loves itit gets pretty cold where im at so this is perfect for him it is very versatile so he can wear it many different ways its so soft and lightweight and breathable yet it still keeps the wind outfits my father great and it looks great as well exactly as described and pictured this mask will also be great in the summer as well seeing as how its lightweight it will be a good sweat stopper when working outside especially since there is so many ways it can be worn also machine washable  i received this product at a discount for my honest and unbiased review everything i have stated is my opinionthings ive experienced with this product i have came across anything negative about this product but if i do i will update my review with that information

review: it took me a little bit to get use to this but once i did i really like it  i dont have to worry about keeping on my shoulder or anything like that  it is very convenient and best of all the husband cant have me put anything in there because there is no room  i would really recommend this to anyone who is looking for a change and something smaller

review: these are the best flip flops ever seriously i mean it  i live austin tx and the flip flop is the unofficial state shoe almost year round however the heat and humidity here can really take a toll on the poor standard flip flop and they burn out at least mine did within a month of being put into use but not havaianas these last for the long haul and their pretty designs do not rub off or fade after repeated wearing  they last so long that it is hard to justify buying more than one pair but i havent let that stop me  if you are looking for a durable pretty little flip flop for the summer  you can do no better than these the price may be a bit more than your standard drug store  variety but havaianas are well and truly worth it

product: mountain made princeton waterproof insulated winter gloves for men and women

review: i ordered these tights for halloween and they say they are one size fits all with a weight range of  i am  should work right not exactly the tights dont even pull all the way up to my waist and when i was putting them on they ran immediately i admit i have a few lbs to lose but i am by no means obese and well within the expected range of fit i would not suggest this for anyone larger than a size  or so based on how much they stretch girth wise vs length wise

review: good price for the number of pieces but i much prefer the traditional retainers with longer side pieces thought i would try both metal and plastic to see which i preferred i already lost all  plastic pieces as they have fallen out during my sleep and are difficult to find as for the metal ones i dont like wearing them because the sides are still visible sometimes when i am wearing them which somewhat defeats the purpose for me i didnt have a problem with the plastic ones being visible since theyre nearly clear the sides are not long enough to grip inside the nose and stay in an upright position to remain unseen yet are still long enough to show when hanging down would maybe repurchase a pack of just the plastic ones and treat them as disposable since i lose them so often but will probably go back to the traditional style of retainer as those last longer for me
product: pierced owl set of  septum ring retainers in  stainless steel and clear acrylic

review: what a fun little purse  compact but bigger than a coin purse with room for cash id credit cards keys lip gloss and a small comb the fuchsia is bright and pretty and the sloth realistic looking and cute  the wrist strap is convenient and the small attached charm is a bonus
product: wristlet ziptop with detachable strap and charm  vegan  wearable art  animals  multipurpose clutch bag purse wallet

review: got thins bag for the gym and so far it is holding up pretty good  the draw strings are nice and comfy and dont really dig into my arm pits like other draw strings bags do it fits me pretty well also and can adjust to fit mostly everyone the american flag is a great way to show your patriotism the quality of the image is also pretty high as i could not see any noticeable pixelation anywhere on this bag would recommend to any one looking for a small bag for the gym or anything else at allthis was provided to me at a promotional price for evaluation purposes but i was under no obligation by the seller or any other party to give this item a favorable review please let me know if you found this review helpful liking it
product: pier  drawstring canvas bag canvas duffel bag for vacation gym and daily usage

review: my first cycling shoes  works and fits as expected  easy to install and easy to clip on and off  very good for beginners like me and cheapmy issues with these clips are that the cleats are made of cheap plastic so after a short walk on them they look really torn up  im afraid to walk on them anymore or the cleats might not clip into the pedals anymore  i think you can buy metal cleats but not sure im a novice herealso these are the  hole type cleats most cycle studios use the  hole type cleats so they arent really useful for using in cycling class  just consider that if youre getting into cycling
product: venzo road bike for shimano spd sl look cycling bicycle shoes  pedals black

review: ive been searching for a wristlet to put a few essentials in and have what i need on the go and to throw in my diaper bag the quality at this price point is unbeatable i can fit my iphone x all my cards cash and lip gloss its been a few weeks now and im still loving the product
product: befen women leather zipper phone wallet with card holdercash pocketwrist strap

review: i love havainas and they are summer staples especially living in california i generally wear a size  and have a wide feet   the  size fits me perfectly each time i personally prefer this original style more than their thinner profile ones as i feel those are less padded and feels too flimsy i wear them in and outside of the house all day without problems i suffer from plantar fasciitis and this doesnt affect it very much even though flip flopsslippahs dont have much arch support the green color i got looks a lil bit like a forest green
product: havaianas womens top flip flop sandal

review: it is a nice bag i am selling them to my students so their books do not get wet in the rain and they can keep them together it is a clear defined keyboard design on the outside it seems tough and though it comes packed in a small plastic clear bag it is a good size bag its a good price for a good bag
product: piano keys music waterproof oxford cloth handbag shoulder tote shopping bag gift

review: i am a solid  and have a tummy hips and am chesty  i got a large now does it show off my curvesyesdoes it clingyes but not enough to warrent concern do i care no its marvelous for travel which is why i bought it as i work often on the road it doesnt wrinkle if you are worried about your jiggly bits showing a slip would solve that
product: peach couture womens summer causal v neck shift  sleeve waist tie shift dress

review: bought this ring to replace my wedding band than had a carbon fiber inlay that was starting to turn yellow i never take off my ring so the yellowing is in part probably from me getting it dirty im happy to turn back to a simpler time and just have a solid ring i dont have to worry about turning colors on me comfortable ring overall id recommend
product: mj metals jewelry  to  white tungsten carbide mirror polished classic wedding ring

review: my  year old daughter was so happy to receive a real lab coat in her words she loves playing vet doctor and occasionally scientist but only had an old button up as a makeshift lab coat she was beyond excited to see all the pockets her last on only had one small one and this has  for all her doctor accessories no more need to choose which ones to carry with her and which to leave in the doc mobileshe can easily button and unbutton with the large buttons on this coat very nice for smaller fingers still learning i had picked a size  with her wearing a size  in clothes this coat runs a little bigger than i had thought however i dont mind at all with an ever growing childoverall i love this working class childs lab coat its made of thick high quality fabric also looking and feeling like a real lab coat its hard to find high quality pretend play items for older taller children it seems as though imaginative play is geared towards the under  crowd and it nice to see something for old kids with imaginations as well were already looking into more scientist accessories as well as some better veterinarian gear i look forward to seeing more from the working class brandi received this product for free or at a highly discounted price in exchange for my honest  unbiased review however all opinions are my own
product: working class kids lab coat durable lab coats for kid scientists doctors

review: my daughter loves this costume but i think i love it even more  it looks much nicer than the packaged costumes in the storematerial feels softer and the overall fit and design is perfect for a little girl not flashy not too short not too tight  ive had so many people compliment this costume it really stands out

review: the shoes are just ok  the shoe actually needs a drawstring at the top not only to make the shoe look better but to keep it on the foot  my son likes to run around in the house with them but the shoes do come off easily so i am skeptical about him wearing them in the water  if it comes off in the waterwhats the point plus more work for me as ill have to do a search and rescue for a shoe

product: fit couture straight leg yoga pant

review: these insoles provide little to no support i have custom made orthotics but needed ones that are a little more flexible for certain shoes these got such great reviews so i figured it was a no brainer as soon as you put weight on the insole in collapses and flattens  no support for your arch i weigh  so its not like its due to my weight also ive been battling a very stubborn knee problem and now some feet problems hence the reason im wearing orthotics if you are looking for something to put your foot ankle and knee into alignment and you have high arches these are not for youneedless to say i reached out to the seller surgical medical source for advice on possibly purchasing another pair that would work better for my foot and they were zero help not friendly and dismissive zero stars for customer service i will never purchase from them again
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: i bought three different socks from seller footsmart and was happy that they sent all of them for the same price as shipping only one  not all sellers do that even when they put all items into one package and ship them together  as for the socks themselves not as impressed  i am glad that i only got one of this stylefirst i dont know how i missed that these socks are primarily acrylic and have no cotton at all  yep that does make for a soft sock  however my past experience with acrylic has not been positive and i take full responsibility for missing that detail  i think i got excited seeing the made in the usa and the overall very positive ratings  the socks fit my wide foot very well and the tops do not cut into my ankles but they are also very thick making my shoes uncomfortable  on really cold nights they will be nice to have but other than that they are too warm for texas  the lack of cotton means they dont breathe at all and i ended up with sweaty feet something i havent experienced in years  luckily they were not very expensive so i wont be overly sad when they have to be thrown away  i expect that to be sooner than most would expect from good socks since just one day of wearing left the socks much more fuzzy on the bottoms than they started off  be sure to launder inside out or they will come out of the dryer looking like you have had them for years

review: it was a little confusing when reading about the description of these sunglasses description says made in usa and if you know a thing or two about rayban theyre italian madethen i contacted a representative and they told me they come from seattle maybe thats what they meant by made in usa but they could be shipped from china and the probability of them being fake was high or if theyre shipped from seattle washington theyd be the real deali dont understand how a company can have their product shipped from two locations  some product genuine and some product notthe reviews on amazon are totally mixed and random many people got fake sunglasses and many people got real ones i decided to take the risk and worst case scenario id get my money back in the event they were not real raybansmine just arrived today so my review is very much fresh and new i own  pairs of raybans sunglasses and eyeglasses so i knew to check the box for the made italy milanomilan check the top left lenses for the engraving of the rb logo make sure the shades dont come in a plastic bag but rather the frames the part that goes behind the ear are protected by a plastic cover the case has to be authentic and have the rayban stampmine had all of these details and i am pleased with my purchase of wellpriced lightweight authentic italian made summer ready raybanswith every purchase on amazon its better to double check with the seller where in fact the item is coming from ask about the authenticity and other concerns that may arisei hope this review was helpful and substantial

review: have been using these for about a week and they do the trick of keeping my ears warm while i listen  ive never used behindthehead earmuffs so they take some getting used to plus they have a selftightening spring inside thats meant to keep them in place but begins to hurt my ears after a while  they are quite warm and sound is quite good  better than earbuds and more comfortable  all in all im pleased with these

product: lasuiveur womens batwing sleeve v neck solid bodycon plus size dress

review: the steel rim to gem ratio is not as depicted from most angles you can only see the rim which was the kind of nose ring i was trying to avoid purchasing but i tried one anyway and discovered that they irritate my skin horriblyat first i thought it was just because they are thicker than im used to wearing but my nose got so sore i had to take the one i was wearing out in less than  minutes i then tried it in my primary ear piercing which has been established and healthy for over  years and very few earrings irritate my primary piercings well in seconds my ear turned red heated up and started to swell needless to say its the metal itself which i had soaked in rubbing alcohol dried and then wiped in alcohol again before using so no factory debris to blamei am returning these and will update on that experience as well

review: i been using these insoles for a few years now and will never wear shoes again without them i am flat footed as a duck and predictably developed plantar factitious in both feet this product help alleviate the pain and has kept me pain free sincekeep in mind however one cannot just throw these in your shoes and wear then all day at first they take getting used to and should only be worn a few hours a day to start and slowly build up to all day wear over about two weeks

review: they are your standard vans slip on shoes they run in the same sizes as my converse so they fit well i tried a pair on in the stores thinking i would wear a  as that is what i would wear in my tennis shoes but that was a bit too big and a  was just too small the  that i got fit perfectlymy left shoe has something like a flaw where the ball of my foot touches when i step down its not like that in the right so i am assuming its just a small flaw but its not a big deal i am sure over time i wont eel this anymorelike converse i cannot wear shoes like this for too long if i were going to walk for a long time i would not wear these shoes but i have trouble wearing shoes with little supporti do like them though dont mind the cat hair in my photos i cant bring anything home without cat hair clinging to it instantly as i bring it in

review: very nice tie  slightly longer than i had hoped but i have a shorter frame than is usual  overall it gives the impression of a perfectly tied tie  the zipper has not snagged at all  i ended up purchased  other colors to change it up a bit  theyve all been of the same quality very much worth the cost to never have to screw up that double windsor that you tied once  years ago and still have the same knot that has slowly gotten a little crooked over the years
product: mens classic zipper tie

review: one reviewer here stated these have no practical purpose  on the contrary i have found they are full of purpose  they are small and fit in a smaller purse or in the glove compartment  they work the same as regular sunglasses with uv protection and they are wraparound so the sun doesnt sneak in when youre making turns  once you put them on they stay put  they gently hug your temples and do the job of expensive sunglasses without the weighti have been given these by my eye doctor for years after dilating my eyes and use them all the time while driving  mine never came with a case or fancy cord like the other reviewer described  they are plain old good common sense to keep on hand whether in the house or in the car  and i like the uva and uvb protection  dont listen to the other reviewer who is just miffed because he didnt get the bells and whistles  these are the real deali have pampered myself with the pair i got from my doctor so ive treated myself to a replacement set
product: etp roll up sunglasses  one size fits all  uva and uvb protection

review: for a very quick introduction i started looking into hard wallets after having snapped countless cards from using leather wallets i debated between a fully i closed wallet like this and the more currently common elastic strapped two panel cars holder wallets with money clips i couldnt decide so i bought one of each this being the enclosed style between the two different styles i prefer this one i feel like my stuff is more secure being enclosed but i do have some concerns which i will list in the pro and con list belowpros compact fully enclosed clicks shut with built in latchnot sure if this is a pro or con so ill leave it in the middle i feel that this wallet is better off being carried in a front pocketcons nothing larger than a credit card will fit so forget carrying business cards or those paper cards some places hand out and stamp every time you come in until you earn a free beverage proof of insurance cards etc it cant hold many bills considering you have to fold them in half twice to fit you cant double up cards without extreme difficulty or stuffing the wallet til it cant close so youre limited to either  cards or maybe  cards if you plan on carrying three or more cash bills this is a two for one the company that listed this product stated that the wallet is rfid blocking yet the they include two rfid blocking card sleeves which leaves me wondering if the wallet itself is actually rfid blocking or if its just the included sleeves that are heres the part  to this con those included sleeves yeah they dont even fit inside the wallet so scratch using those anyway the pre installed card slots inside the wallet feel very cheap and im concerned about how long they will last when latched shut the top and bottom can slide on one another catching the side walls on each other will try to demonstrate in one of the included photosto wrap upas contradictory as it may seem to the pro and con list all in all im actually mostly happy with the wallet sure i had to do some spring cleaning when it came to the contents i would normally carry in a wallet however this wallet allows me to still have my contents fully enclosed and i dont have to worry about elastic straps wearing out over time like i would have to with the money clipcard holder alternatives plus i will no longer have to worry about my cards bending and eventually cracking in half like i have over the last countless years of carrying a standard soft wallet so if your concerns match mine then overall id recommend this wallet

review: use this to help hold and cover my work pants love the tacky edge around the top that helps the band from sliding around i also ordered a generic brand similar to this and the bella band for me was a lot better functioning and quality its really worth the extra money
product: ingrid  isabel womens maternity everyday bellaband

review: i bought this for my  old daughter shes tall for her age and is  and  lbs for halloween and she absolutely loves it in fact she now wears it around the house for pajamas and loungewear its a super soft fleece and on an average woman it still might be a bit tall and saggy but for the average man it should fit just right its also pretty warm we had a cold snap on halloween and she only wore a pair of leggings and a long sleeved shirt underneath and didnt need a coat or anything else as it kept her fairly warm in  degree weather when wearing it inside you will get very toasty so i would recommend just a tank top and shorts if its an inside costume party so you dont end up creating your own personal sweat lodge for the price i was quite pleasantly surprised with the quality and shes definitely getting our moneys worth out of it
product: rg costumes penelope pig

review: i gave this a  tar rating because of two factors one it was very bulky i was looking for something less bulky and two it runs very large i ordered a small and it was huge on me the actual gloves looks to be of good material and product overall i was looking forward to bringing these on my trip especially since thy had a zipper slot for hand warmers  but sadly ill be returning them soon since they dont fit at all
product: mountain made princeton waterproof insulated winter gloves for men and women

review: these have been god sent for my little one who likes to rip his face apart when he gets hungry and to keep strangers from touching his little hands while out and about they definitely stay on always ive never had them fall off not once they are a nice soft cotton material and the grey in my opinion mesh nicely with all his little outfits love them so much he has  of the same grey pair so get at least  pairs because trust meyoull need it

review: almost but not quite for me im a curvy petite   lbs  usually wear an xs or s like pretty much everyone else has said it is extremely cheap fabric think halloween cape for the top and a slightly awkward fit all around the top is super thin and needs to have something under it but i have no clue what cut of a bra could go under it and is still a bit too seethrough for pasties im keeping it for a while in the hopes ill find on occasion to wear it but most likely will end up giving it away further down the line this is a classic example of you get what you pay for

review: ive purchased these shoes before with good success they lasted about a year before there was very visible wear and tear however i purchased a recent pair back in sept  that december the fabric started to tear around the elastic on the left side of the right shoei contacted the seller gbrandshop about a warrantyrefund but they sent me to vans for that vans shut the case down outright stating they only warranty shoes bought through their authorized resellers i was asked to handle it through the amazon shop back to gbrandshop they never responded to another email after the initial finger pointi contacted amazon and got the refund handled through their az policy amazon is the clear winner in customer service here disappointed with vans customer service on this the quality of their shoes hopefully it was just a bad run and especially the customer service of gbrandshop

review: this fits very well  i am heavy busted abd shirts usually are tight on the bust or if i order it large the shirt is shapeless  this fits well and is shaped behind  medium fits perfectlyfits nicely for work  please note their is no shine on it like in the photo it is a bland colour  the green is a tad bit lighter than in the photo
product: edwards ladies lightweight open neck poplin blouse   sleeve

review: absolutely gorgeous corset  made out of some of the best faux leather i have ever seen on a piece of clothing  and looks to be made to last quite a while  im a  ddd and naturally ordered the  i can barely zip it up instead of sending it back  i decided to do my own alteration to it  and see how that goes  the price was reasonable  and i feel the alteration will work for me  considering that there is not a larger size to exchange with  well see how this goes
product: dreamgirl womens plussize beyonce corset and thong set

review: anytime i buy something i always read the reviews before purchasing the item and this was no exception i already had pain in my feet from plantar fasciitis so it was difficult to not want to throw them back in the box and send back if it wasnt for the reviews and giving them a chance because of them i would have sent them back immediately instead i chose to listen and gave them time even with the pain they caused until my feet got used to them it took about or less then a week and i was pain free i cannot stress how difficult it was for me to walk and now i have no pain i can now stand all day at work and not have to cringe every time i walk
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: this is small so grab a size up i like having a really snug top but it is definitely not a breeze to get in or out of i probably could have gotten a size up and still have had the super tight feeling i like if you are not experienced contorting your body and dislocating your joints to get into shape wear without getting deodorant on it go ahead and size up

review: this hat is well made and the fabric is soft and medium thick  it washes well by hand  the only thing that i would like to be improved is thicker or stiffer material in the front  what happens is over time the front will sag and to me it looks funny  i like it to look like the picture when i am wearing it  what i ended up doing  is after i washed it and it was dry i starched the front so it will stand up  it lasts quite awhile but i wish i didnt have to do that  otherwise its a good hat and i wear it every day in the warm weatheri hope this review was helpful to you

review: im still pregnant so i havent worn this yet but wanted to at least start a review because i think there may be serious sizing issues i went to the belly bandit website and used their size calculator i entered my measurements for  weeks and it said get an xl i entered the same measurements for  weeks and it said large i did both weeks because there is some discrepancies with my due date i ended up ordering the large thinking that its better to be a little tight than too large especially given how quickly ill shrink after the baby is herewell the large came and its huge im  or  weeks and i can actually wear it  so even ordering down when in between sizes is clearly not enough i imagine this will work for about a week and then ill need the medium ill update once we get there but heads up even if you are at the tip top of a size range you still may benefit from ordering another size down update my suspicions were right  i was only able to wear this for about a week before it was just ridiculously too large  if you are between sizes or on the lower end of a size i personally would recommend going down a size especially if you want it for more than just a few days after birth on the up side i did find that those first few days when it did fit it helped with that hollow feeling you sometimes get while standing after a delivery i also have diastasis recti and found it helpful in giving me a little support while standing to cook meals etc this was not comfortable when sitting  it would just dig into my ribs sides hips etc fine while standing but sitting was awful

product: rasta imposta crayola

review: i just got my shirt  i was disappointed by the size of the stud holes  theyre regular button hole sized  also there are buttons that i suppose might be used instead of the studs the stud holes on the inside are also buttonhole sized  the problem i was trying to solve was the studs coming unbuttoned due to the holes being the wrong size  i may be able to make it work by closing off some of the button holes
product: tuxedo shirt by neil allyn   cotton wing collar with french cuffs

review: edit looks like they changed the design the old emblem on the front was large and round the new picture is smaler this review may no longer be valid if they changed more than just the emblem my hat is closest to the natural version they sell in  based on the picturesthis sea straw holds up better than the thin stuff they use on the new style of straw hats much stronger stuff a month of rough use and no damage at all so farthe underside has a glued black cotton i think layer to help keep tiny sun spots from shining through the straw making this hat less distracting than my last straw hat the inside has a thin elastic band to make it fit more comfortably no more straw poking my foreheadthe chin cord looks frayed like it was brushed to look old like they do with fashionable jeans these days its softer than most cords because of this less itchy on chin but im concerned it might have reduced the cords lifespanthe brim is so wide that it reduces head range of motion if youre wearing something bulky onaround your backshoulders backpack lifevest seatchair costume but is very light and comfortable otherwise good for yard work and beach not good for kayak fishingthe emblem on the front is ugly and prevents air from moving through the front of the hat but you can cut the stitching on the back and the glue they used is so soft you can gently pull it off from there without hurting the straw no heatgun requiredone year edit i still use this hat one year later ive found it expands too much when it gets soaked so dont use it in the rain it will expand enough that it no longer rests on your head but on your ears and is heavy when soaked with water leaving it to dry it shrank back to the original  size thoughthe steel eyelets for the chinstrap are not stainless or coated they rusted in the presence of salt water ocean use if you take this hat to the beach i suggest you rinse the eyelets to keep them from rusting too much the chinstrap stopper has a steel spring that has rusted too but it still works so farotherwise this hat has held up well enough for a straw hat imo the only damage is on the very top and i blame myself for smacking it on things because im used to being short enough to go under and the hat increases my height several inches
product: oneill mens sonoma prints straw hat

product: jewelrieshop  nose ring hoop stainless steel nose piercing body jewelry set

review: considering i had purchased this as a gift for a female friend i was very worried when i opened the box and could barely see the inscription at first glance the ring looks more like a gold wedding band than anything else in the end i gave it to her but made certain to tell her to look very carefully at it to ensure she didnt freak out i also purchased another ringnbspa datahookproductlinklinked classalinknormal  engraved gold tone ring pendant chain necklace for men women teen girls  from a different listingseller that came with a necklace that once was actually engraved and is much more like the one i expected this to bebtw  the overall quality of the ring seems to be decent and that is why i gave this product  stars instead of

review: i normally wear gold and real diamonds an i have lost more stones from my rings than i can count i have spent more money on replacing stones than i did on the rings themselves  i have given up on them completely i am a very outdoorsy active person i ride horses camp fish hunt etc i purchased this set and i cant be more pleased with what i received it is beautiful extremely durable and trust me i have put it to the test if youre thinking of ordering this set please dont think twice about it just do it its so worth it
product: doublebeez jewelry stainless steel square cubic zirconia solitaire engagement wedding ring set

review: i purchased these for my work boots  my heels would always hurt after a long  hour shift  these powerstep pinnacle insoles helped a little but not fully  my feet would still be extremely sore after being on my feet all day  finally i went to the foot doctor and he advised i have plantar fasciitis  i then received prescription insoles after have my feet measured and molded  luckily my insurance paid for the insoles as they were about   these powerstep insoles are like putting a bandaid on serious problem  if you want a true fix for painful heels go to the foot doctor none of these generic insoles you can buy from the store will compare to the ones you get from the doctor so save your money
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: i bought these as a gift for my dad he loves them he uses them so that he could listen to his books while hes sleeping and his wife doesnt have to hear  he had tried the headbands and the pillow speakers but he found that the headbands stretched and the pillow speakers didnt really muffle the sound enough for his wife to sleep comfortably

review: i knew this item was coming from china so i wasnt sure what to expect  i ordered a slightly different cage bra and it came perfect  this one came without the cup inserts and the hole you insert the cups into on one side is sewn too tightly so the front of that side is slightly bent inward  but nothing a little snip and restitching cant fix  the back is perfect and snug  im a  bought a medium and it fits perfectly  if yours comes with inserts thats awesome if not local fabric stores should have them  if youre fine with the thin fabric between you and world then disregard i just realized this reviews the whole selection of cage bras  the above review is for the one with the cage in the backthe harness bra with the x in the front fit me perfectly without any flaws  the shoulder straps of that one do not stretch so they could cut into your shoulders if you find you need more support  again that bra was a medium

review: i previously gave this item a  star rating due to the fact that the sizing advice in my opinion was bad  since then i have found out that the guidance provided to get a size larger than your size if the ring is a wide ring was allegedly not the guidance of the producer of this product but rather amazon guidance  in my case this was bad guidance having said that the company in question answered all of my questions and is willing to take the ring back for a full refund  i have subsequently ordered another ring in my size because i can and must say the quality is great  as for the return of my first ring i have not decided yet i may keep it just in case my finger gets bigger  additionally once i get the new ring if it fits well i may order a gold plated one in addition to the one i have  good company great ring  i recommend you order you exact size regardless of the width of the ring

review: if you havent tried worlds softest you should  i wear them mostly with western style boots but recently have started wearing them with my golf shoes for winter golf  they do get pretty furry but not to the point of thinning out they are very very durable  i cant recommend them enough  oh and theyre soft

review: these dresses are great for summer  lightweight yet substantial material  i ordered two prints  this one in large and another in xl  both fit but i prefer the xl because i like the extra room especially in the summer  buy one or more you wont be dissatisfied

review: perfect for summer by the beach water parks hiking just about anything under the sun the headband feels sturdy i am more careful with the film everytime i put it inside my bag it feels like it can crack but then so far its still good no cracks no damages i would strongly suggest not to leave it in the car i gave this product  stars bcause of its uv protection and its long term effect against sundamage especially the dry heat from california weather
product: sun visor uv protection hat cap hiking golf tennis outdoor

review: i give this product  stars im   about  im small up top and medium at the bottom i ordered a medium  i would have gotten a small only due to the private area where it has a bunch of space if youre a real skinny girl  no offense  i wouldnt buy it because it will look funny whatever size you normally are i say go down  due to the crotch baggage area but if youre a fuller top and bottom get your exact size because you will definitely fill it out i love it and i plan on getting all the colors in a small since im small at the top it will look less baggyish around the private area   oh and it feels nice and soft ps it also gives serious camel toelol
product: kashani womens empire waist designer slim bandage casual cocktail jumpsuits m

review: best noncustom orthotics on the market  very durable  i have flat feet bone spurs and periodically suffer from plantar fasciitis  the arch is in the perfect location offers amazing support and the heel has just the right amount of cushioning  they are the reason i can walk any distance without aching feet
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: these capris are really nice they are slightly thicker than most legging type capris they fit very well sliding right on with no need for yanking or tugging they fit quite snugly but not tightly they do loosen up the longer you wear them  but they dont sag and they go right back after washing the material is softthese capris also have a hidden pocket it is in the front waistband just to the left of center it holds a key and a couple dollars nicely the pocket is about   deep and a little bigger acrossthe  degree capris are a little longer than many capris ive purchased the have a  inseam and hit my  frame  above the ankle most other capris i purchase are  above the ankle i dont mind this difference i actually like both lengths but someone else might mind the differencei wear a  which usually translates to xl and the xl in these is a perfect fiti received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest review
product: degree by reflex power flex yoga capri  cationic heather activewear pants

review: great fit and quality for the price the wide band is awesome i ordered  colors and my only complaint is the peacock blue is not even close to the image on the site it is actually more like the sea green but even a shade darker than that  i am aware that colors on screen are much different and vibrant than color in person but this was so off that i thought it worth mentioning
product: degree by reflex power flex yoga capri  cationic heather activewear pants

review: these are awesome  they got here early all  were here none broken or missing  now i did get duplicates but i am extremely happy i did as they are for my nipples not my tongue  also i only have  pot leaf ones which makes me happy because id never wear them my loss is my friends gain because many of them will wear them  very happy and satisfied customer
product: lot of   assorted colors mixed tongue rings barbells body piercing nipple jewelry

review: very happy with the purchase  fit true to size  i wear medium size  clothes  my hip and chest are same measurments i could have gone with a medium or large but decided on large because i wanted a looser fit instread of a snug fit  tried  on the dress and it was very nicejust loose enough to feel comfortable  as long as your hips  are not disproportionately out of place compared to your chestthe dress will fit true to the size you normally wear  if you are in between sizes like i ami suggest going with the larger size because flapper dresses are supposed to hang loose not hug your curves
product: california costumes fashion flapper adult costume

review: i suppose this fits as expected im often inbetween l and xl and this is close fitting in a l the blend of materials allows for a nice drape it fits close but not skin tight in any way slightly snugger than the  blend eco mock tanks also from alternative  i do slightly prefer the eco mock  back to this one neck line is good no weird deep plunge bottom is just long enough to work out in without exposing the belly when lifting overhead and not so long youre wearing a tent i have a couple of these and so far no issue retaining odors or pilling from the wash no major wrinkles if you hang it immediately after washing  alternative makes good tank tops
product: alternative mens double ringer tank shirt

review: i purchased this clutch to match silver shoes i had planned to wear to my brothers upcoming wedding  it was quick same day delivery and matched my shoes perfectly  it is also very well made and easy to open  the finger hole at top of the clutch is very stylish and allows half of your finger to fit through  i received compliments on the purse all night  so glad i purchased it  now i need another fancy event to attend so i can use it again
product: fawziya bling ring clutch purse women rhinestone clutch evening bags and clutches

review: i am using these inserts with a sneaker that already has some arch support but i felt that i needed more  got these based on another reviewers recommendation  thus far i am satisfied with these inserts  i have however not tried any other insoles for similar purposes so can not compare withother brands  although i am happy with this one
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: we had recently purchased the protective mittens that had the elastic bands on them  the problem was are little dude kept taking them off in the middle of the night and would continue to scratch his face  weve been using these mittens for  weeks now and they stay on him the whole night  thank god somebody finally found a mitten that stays on  we just put in an order to get  more just in case we loose them
product: baby mittens  cotton baby mittens no scratch great for newborns  months unique strap that keeps mittens in place and your precious baby safe guaranteed best baby gift

review: i like everything about this product i was afraid it might slide off but the rubber strip on the bottom keeps it in place really well i noted that another reviewer bought a size  for prepregancy pant size of  so i went with size  as well and it fits perfectly im only  weeks now so i hope that it still works into the third trimester
product: ingrid  isabel womens maternity everyday bellaband

review: grandson loves it  appears well made  and there are warning labels not to submerge it underwater or wear for protection  has good count down to blast off sounds but no other communications which would have been nice  also the microphone you see is non operational which would also have been nice if it did  however it does have a spring loaded visor that flips up with the push of a button  i would buy this again
product: aeromax jr astronaut helmet with sounds

review: this product saved my life during those early pregnancy months where i was too bloated to zip my pants but also to small to wear maternity pants yet it kept my zipper covered and smoothed out the front of my pants it also lended some support to my back as well  i like that it was very wide it does have some drawback although it has rubber grippy stuff to hold onto your clothes it did roll up a lot i remember one time i leaned over my desk and the band rolled up in the back exposing my backside and undiesmy students were hysterical
product: ingrid  isabel womens maternity everyday bellaband

review: i love these shoes a lot the stitching is a little on the off side  you can totally see glue residue the soles are fine but anyway comfortable i just recommended with socks for better comfort they also came in early i just really hope these last long i wouldnt wear them everyday though i hope they dont fall apart soon or get a deep crease overall great
product: coshare  wedges fashionsneakers taupe suede

review: this chala tote is very well made besides being super cute i wanted a nice large tote with pockets on the exterior and interior and really like this style the strap material is very sturdy as is the denim the bag is made from i also like the zip closure ill likely purchase more items from chala
product: chala carryall tote  toffy dog denim

review: this is the second one ive purchased because it works great i wear  waist slacks and got a size  belt and i have enough to fit through the belts loop the belt is actually stretchable so if you need to make it a little longer you just need to pull on it and it will make it a little longerit stays nice and snug once attached and is easy to fit though loops on pants

review: i tried this exact one on at a halloween shop and realized they ran small im a  and the medium fits me like a glove i love this however it was obvious that this costume sat smushed in a warehouse somewhere and was possibly exposed to heat the skirt part of the costume got miscolored as a result hopefully the wrinkles will come out if i hang it but for a  costume i didnt have high expectations
product: secret wishes deluxe wonder woman costume bluered large

review: i ordered xsmall im around  and slim and it fits just right i own the venture windbreaker from north face and this is a great cheaper alternative the fit is slimmer compared to the venture jacket which may be a problem for those who like to layer i hardly wear sweatshirts under my windbreakers so this isnt a problem for me however the sleeves are a bit shorter than the venture i have long arms it keeps me dry the hood is great and i havent seen any damage to the pockets or jackets after a few months of owning this
product: columbia womens arcadia ii waterproof rain jacket

review: these earrings are amazing theyre fairly big around the size of an american quarter by my estimates and seemed rugged and durable also its an officially licensed product which is always a plus i would definitely recommend that anyone interested in this particular jewelry to go ahead an order one or more pairs for you and your friendsfamily theyre super cute and will definitely garner some positive attentionconclusion this product is a diamond in the rough a
product: jinx minecraft diamond ore pendant earrings

review: this shirt just came today actually before the estimated delivery time i was really excited until i took it out of the bagthe fabric is stretchy soft and comfortable but not the way the fabric looks in the photo i ordered an xlarge to be safe im large in the chest area could have gotten away with a large  but i like a looser fitthe problem is the length not at all what the photo portrays this is basically a belly shirt for me very disappointed there the photo makes it look like its a little long in the front and back coming up a little on the sides my shirt was not made that way lol doesnt even touch the top of my pants
product: alabela women sexy sleeveless loose vest tank tops american flag usmasialwhite

review: i wish more stores would carry these socks  rei used to but they dont any more at least in our store and we cant order them  they are thin on the top and have extra padding underneath right where you need it  they also have a higher cuff than many runningsport socks so they stay up and dont crunch under your heel  hope wigwam continues to produce them
product: wigwam unisex coollite pro quarter length sock

review: i love my nightgown the fabric is a tshirty jersey soft and stretchy and the print is lovely the neck has a drawstring that lets me adjust how modest the neckline is i just hope it doesnt shrink very much the fit is not as loose as one might expect in a medium if you wear size  pants you might opt for a large here
product: womens nightgown sleeveless cotton pajamas  sleepwear nightshirt

review: they are perfect  i got all except the light pink and its exactly what i wanted  i would say ill buy this again but there really is no reason when i already have them and they dont break easy ive bit down on it so many times and it still stands i currently have in the black one
product: body accentz  ultra sparkle acrylic tongue nipple ring   in assorted

review: this is the hatlightweight easy to make fit just right on the little ones head and terrific protection  the sixmonthstoeighteenmonth size fits my sixmonthold granddaughter with plenty of room for that brain of hers to grow  shes had so many compliments  apply a little charm as you tie the thing under babys chin and youre all set to enjoy the day  we bought twoone in red one in pinkwell worth the price

review: the print on this dress was super cute but it was so long it just hit at all the wrong spots i am  and normally wear a  i got this in a large to make sure i had room in the chest which was fine but the dress came down halfway past me knees and was just not flattering would probably work well for those girls who are blessed with a few more inches of height than myself
product: switchblade stiletto womens annabella dress

review: i received the celeste color in medium as a gift after wearing it i decided to purchase another color in a large from baby be mines website they have some great sales on clearance items so i took advantage of that  the large size hasnt arrived yet so this is just based on the medium  i plan to wear these at the hospital and for home to sleep in or wear around the house while nursingthe reason i went up a size is mostly for the top area the rest of the gown below the chest fits me alright even at almost  weeks  i am about  currently  lb and   the chest is snug but not overly constraining  its the sleeves that get me  i keep pulling the sides of the gown down because the elastic around the under arm sits too high and irritates my already sensitive skin i hope that with time the elasticity relaxes a bit and becomes more comfortablethe fabric isnt extremely soft but got better after just one wash i did not put the medium size in the dryer due to fear of it shrinking and no longer fitting mei think these are slightly overpriced for the quality of the material and the amount of appealing patternscolors available more variety and darker colors would be nice but they are worth it if you find them on sale or are receiving them as gifts
product: baby be mine  in  nursing nightgown sleeveless hospital bag must have pregnancy and breastfeeding

review: this is my favorite  ring  very happy with it the stone is a bit loose im noticing  but other than that it is a great fashion ring has not turned finger colored yet have had it  months   i am pleased  with it thus far
product: psiroy womens  sterling silver  created pink topaz filled cocktail promise ring

review: very poor quality i have worn these hose for at least  years but these are a big change from all those i have purchased in the past the fabric is very course scratchy and seem to have reduced stretch most disappointing  they run so easily and even have had runs before i put them on  pairs so far have been defective prior to wearing dont buy these
product: leggs leggs control top support panty hose  pair pack

review: the case is good and strong  the carabiner which really is just a small clip however came off with the lightest of tug on the first day of use  it was sewed on with a few small threads that shredded quickly  no big deal for me but if youre going to use the carabiner  thats something to think about
product: uxcell black zipper box bag reading glasses sunglasses case w carabiner hook

review: i ordered chicago bears football slippers and got baltimore orioles baseball slippers i can see how someone who packaged these got it wrong because they are both orange and it just slipped by one of the workers the sticker on the plastic bag says bears so it was whoever stuffed the bags mistakes happen i consider myself lucky that this is my first wrong order after many thousands of dollars spent on amazon amazon quickly sent me out a return label that i printed out i never got around to sending them back and ill just keep them for backup slippers at least they are orange anyways the slippers are warm and comfortable id recommend them providing one gets the team they want
product: nfl chicago bears mens big logo slipper

review: i am   pounds and i ordered the small i wore it over a sweater in a light rain yesterday and it kept me completely dry  helped as a windbreaker too i like that the wrists velcro tight to keep out the rain i like that the pockets have a zipper the reason i knocked off one star is because i had difficulty in the hood staying up on its own
product: columbia womens arcadia ii waterproof rain jacket

review: darling print pretty colors and i love the snaps all the way up the front because they make it easy to put in a squirming infant i just wish it were longer  i love that its made of organic materials  that is precisely why i bought it in addition to the cute design
product: finn  emma organic cotton convertible gowncoverall for baby boy or girl

review: over a year ago i lost my ring when i was swimming and wanted to get a simple band to replace it this one is perfect not too thick but not too think it looks natural on my finger i love that it doesnt rust and basically i never need to take this ring off i recommend getting tungsten carbide since it does not scratch itll last forever love it
product: mj metals jewelry  to  white tungsten carbide mirror polished classic wedding ring

review: purchased these in march my daughter started wearing them in may about twice a week for school and the front seam is already detached from the body of the shoe  i would love to exchange for a new pair but the return window has closed  i feel like the product is defective
product: nike baby boys downshifter  athletic shoes

review: sizing is weird some people say this had is way to big but i got the  hat for my  year old that is the size of a three year old and the hat seems to small the brim is bigger witch is nice for face coverage but its still seems small
product: i play girls baby brim sun protection hat aqua shellflowers

review: the band looks like it will work but the instructions told me to use my  month measurements to order well i did but the band was extremely too large to use after giving birth so maybe use your  month measurement ive reordered a smaller size and will see what happens
product: belly bandit original postpartum belly wrap

review: i have fotl boxer briefs and love themeven more than one of those highpriced deals you hear advertised on the radio yes i purchased one of those just to find out the fotls are just as good and a fraction of the price anyhow i ordered these briefs in large and they are just a tiny bit on the big side but hoping that will be corrected after the initial washing also it was a pack of four and the very first pair out of the package had a small hole in itquality control people as long as the other ones are defectfree and i get a little shrinkage in the wash i will be satisfied
product: fruit of the loom mens breathable brief multipack

review: super comfy i wear these to work everyday they are indeed true to size at first of course theyre going to be too tight theyre brand new shoes you have to break them in after a few days they dont feel too bad and even better after a few months
product: vans adult classic slipon checkerboard blackpewter

review: very cool glasses i love everything about them and so does everybody else i know that wants to try them on anyways the price is right they fit well dont look or feel like cheap sunglasses but they literally are i got these for around  and free shipping i call these my bob welch glasses  a  singer who sang ebony eyes watch the video on youtube youll see i proudly give these glasses  stars
product: funoc retro vintage fashion unisex round arrow style metal frame sunglasses eyewear

review: i developed plantar fasciitis a couple of months ago and these inserts were recommended by some pro runners at fleet feetlocal athletic store the inserts provide great support and have really cut down on the pain ive experience in the past  i also tape my heel which im sure cuts down on the pressure that is applied to my heeli would recommend these inserts to anyone who has problems with plantar fasciitispsgreat customer service  i had a question about my purchase and they got back to me very quickly  fast shipping too
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: i got a pair of these for my son years ago  the recommendation of his podiatrist they worked well and he eventually told me that they were showing signs of wear and getting small i was surprised to look back at my records an see how long they lasted they do what the podiatrist said they would and had they not worked im sure i would have needed to have taken my son back for follow up visits  they fall short of what custom orthotics will do and for some sizes they can be expensive but they are generally a good value
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: i am currently  weeks postpartum and i feel that the belly bandit has been very helpful at getting my prepregnancy stomach back  i started wearing it the second day after my daughter was born and i usually wear it both day and night  my husband and family have also noticed how well it seems to be doing  i gave it  stars because like other reviews said it does not lay flat and can be seen under certain outfits  ill usually still wear it anyway because depending on if i suck it in or wear a looser shirt it isnt that noticeable  i would definitely use this product again with another pregnancy and will continue to wear it with this oneupdate i have come to notice that if the product has become loose after wearing it a while you can take it off for a few hours and it will tighten back up
product: belly bandit original postpartum belly wrap

review: absolutely excellent ring in every possible way i have not removed this ring since i received it  i work play bathe sleep with it on it incredibly comfortable i have never had a ring that feels this way and it is beautiful to boot the price on this ring is truly mind boggling bec the quality is beyond anything ive purchased for the same amount of money or even quadruple that amount seriously to add to all this this came very quickly was packaged well toothis is actually my second ring from them the first one was slightly less wide than this which i truly loved as well and wore every day upon getting it goes to show how much i love it when i wear two of them at the same time all the time literallyhighly recommend this gorgeous ring
product: mj metals jewelry  to  white tungsten carbide mirror polished classic wedding ring

review: product arrived quickly i chose expedited shipping and was well packaged by seller  its a travel wedding set so i dont lose my wedding ring in the ocean  the set fits together well  i was surprised that the engagement ring wasnt flat against the guard  when i looked more closely at the photo its the same ring  the engagement ring curves in a little to meet the center stone but the guard is straight acrossas for the workmanship there is a little divot the size of a pin tip toward the inside of the guard  once the engagement ring is set inside the center stone happens to cover it up so its not worth returningits beautiful
product: ct solitaire roundshape cubic zirconia cz bridal engagement wedding ring guard set center stone  ct

review: it is as described  wish there was more description of the product  for example it is gold plated  but what is the gold planting overlaying  silver  not sure also the size is a little to tight i normally do take a  but it doesnt expand as much as my other rings do i guess you get what you pay for  the ring other wise is beautiful if your looking for a promise ring or just a ring that is something that is lovely highly recommend  but would like more details before buying
product: tivani eternity love womens pretty  rose gold plated solitaire cz crystal engagement rings set best promise rings for her anniversary wedding bands collection jewelry rings

review: gorgeous ring i am an  and thats the size i ordered perfect fit i personally love stainless steel because it stays shiny thing ring does not disappoint i wasnt expecting it to be as big as it is and still look so real i added photos of it next to a penny to give perspective
product: ct round cut cubic zirconia stainless steel wedding ring set womens sz

review: my daughter was  months old when i got this hat about  months ago to go on vacation in guam she wore this to the beach multiple times her growth percentiles are normally smaller to midrange her head circumference is in the  percentile she is  months now and the hat still fits perfectly with room to grow there is a little stretchy part that goes around her head and you can tie it to be tighter or let it out if your baby has a bigger head she normally does not like to wear hats or sunglasses but she kept this on the entire time we were at the beach it keeps the sun out of her eyes because it droops ever so slightly and is made of a light cotton material but will still hold up to multiple washes the inner part is lined with mesh and i suppose it helps to add a layer of fabric yet still keep the baby cool i would recommend this little hat to anyone and i think it is a great value for what i paid and will hold up well for future use

product: hi sprout toddler baby waterproof sleeved bib bib with sleevespocket  months

review: this ring is extremely comfort looks very nice and im beyond happy about my purchase  i work in a hospital and this is perfect for everyday wear and i dont have to worry about my wedding band becoming damaged  my normal ring size is  but with this ring i had to return that size and i tried a  which fits very well  one satisfied customer overall
product: mj metals jewelry  to  white tungsten carbide mirror polished classic wedding ring

review: lots of stretch in calves length will bring the top all the way to the bottom of the kneecap foot is generous  i have several different pairs that come out of the wash just as nice as they went in and show no ill effects from drying on medium heat  love the fact that the socks are mirrorimages of oneanother so you can have the same design showing on both sides
product: sock it to me zebra womens knee high sockssize

review: the shorts fit fine and they serve the purpose but they seem a bit insubstantial and plain for my taste  though the product description probably said they have no pockets i wish now that they had pockets or that i had ordered shorts with pockets  the mesh seems to breathe well but it also leaves them feeling like less of a short than i was expecting  im not suggesting that they are not a good short for the right personpurpose but i would not buy them over again
product: alo mens mesh  short sport navy medium

review: ive had issues with boots giving me blisters for my entire life  my last pair of boots i had for over  years and gave me blisters every time  i train  run trails  miles in vibrams but couldnt find a good shoe for when i get off the trail and in more rugged terrain  went looking for a zero drop boot and found these  at first i got blisters fairly quickly and had my doubts that this boot would work at all  but after wearing them in ive found them to be the most comfortable hiking boot ive ever had  im less than  years old and have been an avid hiker since about age  so ive had plenty of opportunity to test out different boots in all price ranges  these have been the absolute best hands down  i highly recommend them to anybody who trains in vibrams but needs a more rugged boot for hunting fishing backpacking etc  i cant speak to law enforcement or military duty use  but for my purposes theyre great  best of all my wife says they dont look like a military boot when i wear them with jeans so i dont mind wearing them in public places  i plan to coat them with beeswax or some other waterproofing material  i only wish that they would make them with a waterproofing liner gortex or something like it to make it waterproof  some reviews advised buying a size smaller or larger than normal  for me it was spot on size   the  and  were too big
product: tactical research belleville minimil transition boot  dm us desert tan

review: large pants are the same length as the xlarge pants the difference is the waist i bought some pants for my wife on the expectation of them been smaller but they were too long for my wife to use the quality of the pants has also gone down from  years ago and these pants are no longer worth even  i will no longer buy them
product: hanes mens ecosmart fleece sweatpant

review: who wouldnt want this horse mask it reeks of latex when you first receive it and i could hardly breathe in it but i just soaked it in some hot water without getting the fur wet and that worked pretty well for it good investment for scaring kids and the elderly
product: ace martial arts supply horse head mask

review: cute little boots it was a gift to our nephew and they fit him great they look very sturdy and should last him a long time the print in the boots are well defined so they dont look cheap i recommend these for anyone youd like to get them for
product: oaki kids rubber rain boots with easyon handles for children  toddlers

review: updatedtwo years later these are still perfect in my daughters ears once we got them in weve only removed them a few times to clean no issues at all with these earrings love them and am irdering a  pair for my  babythese earrings are perfect exactly as described and fit my  month old without being too big or too small i was worried the edges of the wings would catch on her clothes or blanket but they are very smooth and because of the screw backs the earrings lay really close to her ears peace of mind knowing theyre not going to irritate her ears with the real gold too the only tiny problem i had is that because they are so small and the backs are too it took me several tries to get the backs on before i could actually screw them on
product: ritastephens childrens  real gold baby butterfly post stud screw back cubic zirconia small earrings

review: this hat worked out well for a marching band costume but i made some changes to better work with my blue and white band uniform  i used model paint to change the gold medallion to silver replaced the black feather to white ostrich feathers which were longer and straighter and added a small silver chain from a hardware store to the bill of the hat  voilathe quality and price of the hat are good but i wished there were other color options the bill had two dents in it when it arrived but i was able to pop them out  the material is substantial stiff and felty and it took some effort to get a needle through to attach the chain i added as to size i have a small head and it was loose so i tipped it back and it rested on my glasses temples  worked just fine
product: dress up america kids big red marching band hat one size fits mone sizet

review: i purchased this pin to use the ribbon pin for an award medal i wanted to change from a necklace to a pin the ribbon is slightly smaller than i thought it would be but will work well enough until the pin i need becomes available again definitely worth what i paid for it
product: dtrading saint gerard patron of expectant mothers medal on bow lapel pin with prayer card

review: i washed it first as i do for all clothing items  very comfortable and soft  one complaint is that when i covered my nose and wore my glasses my nasal breath escaped through the to of the front and fogged my glasses  otherwise it kept me comfortable
product: super z outlet fleece windproof ski face mask balaclavas hood

review: i wanted to get a good hat for our new baby boy that would last him and put up with some regular wear and tear were stationed in the middle east and hats are a  days requirement  in terms of size it is big i bought grey and aqua and ive put the aqua one on our nearly  old it also washes well and the ties stay tiedmy only critique is the buckle on the back to adjust the fit adjustable fit is good but the buckle would be better on the front centre as it is i have to remove the hat anytime our son is in his stroller or car seat so he doesnt have a plastic lump in the back of his head so i still have to provide him alternative sun protection

review: these headbands are super adorable with a really cute design and fresh fun floral prints they are a perfect size for my  month old and my five year old is also able to wear them but they seem a little bit too tight for her my only complaint is that the seams are not sewn together very nicely in the back  they arent fished and the raw edges werent hidden in any way so i feel like that makes them seem a little cheaply donei received the quest sweet baby girl headbands at a discount in return for an honest and unbiased review i was not paid compensated or otherwise influenced in any way to give a positive rating i do not have any type of relationship with seller vendor or manufacturer beyond that of a normal consumer i give out my ratings based on my personal experience my impressions are based upon my personal testing of this product  if you found my review helpful would you let me know

review: the only piece of the costume that wasnt quite as expected was the belt piece its a foam piece with gold paint on one side and it is not attached as it seems to be in the picture therefore it moves around as its worn going either above or below the seam between the skirt and the top i wish this had been a sewn on part of the ensemble otherwise this costume looks great

review: this ring is very durable and extremely scratch resistant i ordered one  years ago and wore it everyday up until a day ago when out of the blue my finger swelled up for no apparent reason my husband and i tried absolutely everything to get it off my swollen finger including using a dermal saw to try and sand it down and among other werid things never left a single mark in it so i ended up having to go to the hospital they had to literally find the jaws of life to cut this ring off so i can truthfully say this ring will with stand anything and i already ordered a new one a size up since my old one is now sadly in three pieces but overall definitely a great ring u want something durable and scratch resistant and visually great looking this is it

review: i purchased this in the hopes that it would allow me to avoid buying maternity pants but i ended up returning it after wearing it for less than a week in my experience the bellaband would not stay put which made it totally ineffective at holding up my pants every time i sat downat home in the car at a restaurant etcit got pushed up and out of position so every single time i stood up i had to reposition the thing over my pants waistband it was a big hassle think about how many times you sit down and stand up in a day and i just didnt have the patience for it i know that many women really like this product and that it works for them thats greatit might work for you and save you a bunch of money maternity clothes are so ridiculously expensive all im saying is that i dont think its the best solution for every pregnant belly out there
product: ingrid  isabel womens maternity everyday bellaband

review: it is getting the job done for the most part this jacket does nothing for warmth it is purely a rain jacket i dislike the hood it would work more efficiently if the drawstrings were easier to tie to keep the hood up in the rain im not a fan of the mesh inner lining but it serves its purpose of being light weight

review: i only gave this product a  star because i just received it so do not as of yet know how it will fair over time as of now i can say it arrived on time and looks beautiful after examining the jacket closely i can say it does have its imperfections but nothing worth complaining about because they really arent noticeable unless you really are looking for something but hey normal wear and tare could cause a lot worse the sizing is somewhat small after reading the reviews i went with a xxl because this is what i normally wear and it gives me some space but to parrot another persons description it fits like a glove which if riding can be a very good thing just dont try wearing anything to heavy underneath i would also not recommend wearing it out on a bike on a real cold day because it is lightweight which is what i was looking for all in all i do love this jacket so far
product: diamond plate ladies rock design genuine buffalo leather motorcycle jacket

review: update after figuring out sizing the shoes worked great my daughter ended up wearing the size  last summer the size  during a winter vacation but not the size  is too small for her chubby feet she cant get the shoes on but it looks like lengthwise it could maybe fit either way i bought the size  for the summer shes wearing a  at stride rite now anyway and will update if they dont fiti cant comment on how well they work just yet but i did want to comment on sizing in case it helps someone else i read a review where someone mentioned their child wore a size  so they sized up to  and it worked perfectlywell my child wears size  at stride rite i bought the  and its much too big my daughter definitely has chubby thick feet and i think water shoes should fit snugly but these were loose on her and definitely too long i bought a size  and can update my review when it arrives they seem to be of decent quality look pretty nice and have a good grip so i decided to keep the size  for the future anywayand the royal blue color is beautiful who says girls have to wear pink
product: i play kids  baby water shoes aqua
