review: these are the only swim bottoms i buy eliminating the expense of disposable swim diapers  pricey bathing suits they do fit true to size but are especially snug around the leg holes which effectively prevents leakage ive cleaned accidents in public bathrooms  its simple enough to unsnap flush  rinse out its easier to get them off even when wet using the snap side  the bright colors can be worn with solid rash guard tops the only downside is since theyre super absorbent they take a long time to dripdry if youre not using a dryer
product: i play boys snap reusable absorbent swimsuit diaper light blue sailboat

review: i bought one of these nearly  years ago to use as a college student i abused this thing for two years while lugging it around full of heavy accounting textbooks while it has seen much gentler use during the past  years i still use it often i also throw it in the washer on occasion particularly if ive spilled something on or more likely inside it unless you look at it closely it still looks new and im sure i have years of life left in this bag it only has one compartment with a zipper the rest being open but for the flap and thats never been a problem for me personally thats the only reason i could see someone deducting even a single star from this bag so i thought i should at least mention itbeing a poor college student when i purchased this i was very hesitant simply because i could purchase something functional for less than half the price but its also one of those purchases that has given me far far more value than i ever would have thought possible at the time if this bag suits your needs you should feel no hesitation in purchasing one immediately
product: manhattan portage dj bag

review: well since reviews said it was smaller than expected i actually ordered a  when i am normally a medium or large in tops the body fit okay but sleeves were quite long pretty flimsy material with black ink writing not great quality and not worth the price i would have been better off trying to find a grease type knock off jacket at goodwill
product: retro  pink lady jacket fancy dress  halloween costume

review: i have had this wallet for a few months now and it is still running strong i am a minimalist so i wanted to put both my apartment key and my wallet items without having to hold a keychain  wallet this was the perfect fit crabby offers a leather canvas or the classic option but i opted to go with the leather wallet for the premium feel the grey leather that i purchased has stained a bit from use but that is expected the strap is a very nice touch both functionally and aesthetically which is great i have no major cons with this wallet i love it
product: leather crabby wallet

review: my second time order  the first one proved very strong and well fitting with ample room around the arm hole  the length is great and long  i am  feet tall and this shirt covers all front to the crotch end and almost down to the bottom of my butt  thick cotton good for house work
product: hanes womens  oz tagless vneck tshirt white l

review: this little id case is great for when you just want something small to carry in your pocket the id window is actually inside the zipped pouch which i like a lot others i have owned  the clear window was outside and i was always concerned about losing my license
product: vera bradley zip id case

review: i cant tell you how fantactic these are i would suggest them to anyone who had toddlers in the pool they are not super bulky like people imagine with cloth diapers the snaps on the side are a must i had a few  and the diaper contained them no problem i used them on my little lady and little man at the same time and no leaks bunches or discomfort such a money saver i would highly recommend
product: i play baby reusable absorbent swim diapers  pack whitelime sealife  months

review: these hats are not completely lined inside and therefore not as warm as they look warm but not as warm as they appear to be in photos also they are cheaply made and the white fuzzy lining comes out easily outside of that they look adorable on are great for photos hold up in the wash do not put in dryer and fit the heads of my  month old as well as my  year old
product: xiaonibang  baby toddler kids cute hat wool knitted winter warm cap pink

review: my son loves these shoes for playing in the water i love these shoes to keep his feet safer while he plays in the water they fit really well with a nice bottom to them they have some grip and a bit of thickness on the bottom like a light sneaker might and they arent overly heavy
product: i play kids  baby water shoes aqua

review: after a diamond had fallen out and was lost for the second time my wife and i had enough of paying  each time to replacerepair my wifes original tiffany wedding band a  ring and it only lasted seven years i guess the makers thought our marriage would include a sevenyear inch and fail as well my wife loved this white tungsten carbide ring saying it is exactly what i wanted it looks as good if not better than my platinum band i would recommend this ring to anyone if you think you may lose it buy two you cant beat the price
product: mj metals jewelry  to  white tungsten carbide mirror polished classic wedding ring

review: pretty sure this is the counterfeit version the neck is way too short to cover your actual neck i bought this because its fairly cheaper than the real one but ended up threw it away and bought the real one which is like  but you can see the significant difference in terms of the quality of painting hair shape and it has longer neck totally worth it i strongly recommend you guys to go for the real one if you planned to wear it to a party or halloween unless youre just buying some silly gift for a little kid

review: recieved it earlier than expected looked at the photos of other buyers and the bottoms with print were not similar other had the stitching hidden while i had stitching that was visible usually im a small so ordered a small and top fit perfect bottoms are tight but it doesnt look odd but good purchase for   material is swimsuit material as well
product: gritu womens halter tankini two piece high neck bikini beach swimsuit beachwear

review: love this driving cap in blue chambray color it is well made and fits pretty well has adjustable side tabs the bill is reinforced for all the hat tipping you are liable to be doing  my son looks very handsome when wearing and gets quite the attention from the ladies  i think the older ladies appreciate the hat tipping the most as it hearkens back to a romantic and polite era  it is indeed a better look than the usual ball cap he switched his preferred style after visiting the british isleslucky for me i was offered a promotional discount for purchase in return for and honest review  i am quite happy to be able to say that the review might not actually do the cap justice  it is definitey one of the best on line hat purchases i have ever made
product: il caldo adult peaked newsboy cap beret sun hat

review: this is a really attractive sweater and the fit flatters however as the owner of several other aran crafts sweaters that wear like iron i am disappointed that this is on the delicate side maybe its the merino wool which is softer than the admittedly somewhat scratchy wool in my other aran crafts garments or maybe its the fabric which is less dense than that of the other aran crafts in my closet but this snags on everything and after a couple of weeks of moderate wear the fabric is pilling where the undersides of the arms brush the sides of the bodyi would return it but its just too darn pretty to part with
product: aran crafts womens double collar coat xlarge charcoal

review: the bellaband is a must have item  it has allowed me to save so much money by allowing me to wear the pants i already own  this band keeps my pantsjeans up even though i cant zip or even button them  it stays in place all day and is versatile for all stages of pregancy and postpartum for that inbetween time when im too big for my regular clothes and not big enough for maternity
product: ingrid  isabel womens maternity everyday bellaband

review: i have finally had opportunity to wear my new mountain made gloves  they certainly are beautiful and love the zipper pockets  unfortunately they are not warm at all  i am so disappointedi wore them outside during  degree weather and within half an hour of talking with a neighbor my fingers were frozeni gave them another try last weekend when we had our first snowstorm and i had  inches of snow to move  it was in the teens and my hands did not last  minutes  my fingers were absolutely frozen to the point of considerable pain  i came in to let my hands thaw out and had to layer other cheaper gloves together to try to just get through an hour of shovelingi really expected more based on the research i did  my hands are sensitive to cold that is why i look intently into any glove i consideri love the styling and features and the white and black color but im afraid i will have to return these and continue my searchwish i could give you a better review
product: mountain made princeton waterproof insulated winter gloves for men and women

review: these are great inexpensive reading glasses  the lenses are clear as a bell and they are quite comfortable  heck they are even a bit stylish  yesterday one of my patients asked me if i had new glasses and before i could reply said they really look good on you  im sold  if you are like me and often forget where you left your reading glasses buying them in sets of six is the only way to go  i should note however that my set were all of the same color unlike the amazon photo of the product depicts  very highly recommended
product: extra pair value eyes plastic frames  pack  incredible value

review: very comfortable but price is too high for something that is now put together very well the sewing isnt great and i returned two of these before getting a third one the first two looked like the sewing was coming undone in places ill attach a picture i really have to say though that i loved how soft and comfortable it is and i kept it even though i felt the price is way higher than it should be for the quality its too bad that this couldnt be cheaper if only because the sewing quality is bad and will probably not last long unless hand washed
product: everly grey womens roxanne  piece maternity and nursing pj pant set with robe and matching baby gown

review: i bought this for my wife because she saw it in one of those cutesy gift stores  when i went to purchase it someone has bought it  so i decided to order this online  well my wife liked the shape and color but it is not made very well  there are loose strings and the handle is coming apart in summary cute purse but its made poorly and last two weeks
product: catherine lillywhite   in turquoise tote bag

review: not nearly as slim as id hoped the middle pocket is pretty useless to me but i knew it was there in advance id just hoped theyd used a thinner material as the bottom liner on it so the one sewn end wouldnt be so much thicker than the rest of the wallet
product: dopp leather rfid protected front pocket wallet slim minimalist wallet getaway id credit card holder

review: you cant beat this deal you get pedals and shoes for a cheap price i get it that they may not be the highest quality products but i did not want to spend a few hundred dollars on shoes and pedals and then decide i didnt like riding with them thats why i ordered these i know these are meant for mountain bikes but i installed the pedals on my road bike i already had compatible pedals on my mountain bike so i get to use the shoes for both bikes been using them for about  months and have been very happy with them i am considering ordering another set definitely recommend these
product: venzo mountain bike bicycle cycling shimano spd shoes  pedals  cleats

review: adorable  sizing is adjustable so this fit multiple kids age  and probably would fit even beyond  super cute print with vibrant color  the fabric was soft yet sturdy cant say enough good things about this purchase got lots of sun and ocean water exposure and did not fade  washed great  very impressed with this purchase and i plan to buy other colors
product: i play girls baby bucket sun protection hat aqua angelfish

review: i was going to wait to write a review of the columbia womens arcadia ii jacket until i tested it in a good rainbut it seems to have warded off bad weather so i havent been able to do it yet  it worked fine when i wore it during a small  shower it looks nice better than many waterproof jackets and the material is not too stiff and it fits fine too  it arrived when expected and is what i hoped it would be it works as a windbreaker as well so if it continues to keep away rain storms that would be fine too
product: columbia womens arcadia ii waterproof rain jacket

review: i bought four of these  sterling silver heart love bracelets as an addon order to other things i was getting from amazon nobody offered me anything in return for this review and although i got them at a nice discount as part of the addon they were not discounted in exchange for a review im simply reviewing them here for the benefit of others who might be interested in ordering them the bracelet is cute and the chain fit easily over my wrist which is a normal american womansized wrist see photo its not a jewelry store quality braceletbut then i was expecting jewelry store jewelry when i bought it it simply is a nice little accessory that you could wear for everyday casual looks or give to a young lady who isnt quite old enough for the real stuff yet personally i gave my four bracelets to four ladies who had helped me put on a volunteer halloween party for a local organization a small trinket but nicely appreciated its something they can wear while they work as waitresses without worrying about losing or breaking something terribly valuable for the price its a nice item
product: fashion brand  sterling silver heart love chain bracelet

review: this top fit great i love the length of the sleeves and the way the rest of the top fits  it looks great with a tank underneath it  id like it a bit better if it wasnt quite so sheer but that is the only complaint i have about this top  the colors and the pattern are beautiful  got lots of compliments on this
product: cocobla women boat neck loose dolman sleeve tops bohemian chiffon blouse t shirt

review: this ring is absolutely gorgeous and worth much more than you pay for it after losing more than one very expensive rings we decided to go with these and never feel guilty if one gets misplaced i think weve each had three get compliments all the time great ring  great value
product: frank sburton   celtic tungsten rings for men women dragon design tungsten carbide wedding band comfort fit size

review: this costume was cut in a very strange way i am about  feet tall and the skirt barely covered my backside called the company to try and send it back but they only exchange and they are out of the next size up  thats what i get for ordering costumes online im out
product: charades womens deluxe beer garden girl costume dress with petticoat

review: we live in florida and have a one year old grandson  he is now walking and loves being outside  we needed a wide brim hat to protect him as much as possible with the sun here  this one is great  love the ability to adjust size of head fit and the soft string tie under chin  baby looks adorable in it but best of all it covers so well and it light weight so his head doesnt seem to sweat too  will be purchasing again as he out grows this one

review: i hate shopping for hats because most stores carry only those with somebodys logo on it i do not want to be a walking billboard for a sports team or product and have to pay the royalty for the privilege of doing so no thanks plain and simple does it for me
product: port  company brushed twill low profile cap maroon

review: my supposedly size  was closer to a   belt  i guess an inch shorter might be appropriate compared to a nonstretch belts but  is too muchit is elastic and has no holes you poke the clasp through the weave so it does fit my  waist ok but requires a bit more stretch than i would prefer with a tucked in shirt and it leaves only a short tab beyond the buckle  it is easily the shortest belt on my rack
product: dockers mens braided canvas web belt

review: i had a pair of these that i had  plus years and adored them  i recently lost one and could not find replacements in the stores  i finally looked on amazon i ordered a pair not having much hope that they would be as good as the originals but i was pleasantly surprised  i think they may be even warmer than the originals  love love love these  i ordered a second black sparkly pair so i have a spare

review: does a great job i have a pair of hiking boots and the left one is inexplicably too narrow and is painful  i put the stretcher in and forgot about it i came back a week later and the boot is noticeably less tight on my foot  i did not use any of the pressure relief plugs however when first experimenting with it i did put one of the plugs on the spot where the boot had felt tight when i cranked out the stretcher i saw a noticeable bulge on the outside of the boot in the place i had the pressure plug i thought that might not be good for the boot so i took out the plug and decided to try it without the plugs and it worked fine  i did not have a problem with the stretcher slipping back in the boot as others have but i could see how that could happen depending on the style and design of the particular boot  one caution i would offer is to be careful and dont overstretch initially  once you insert the stretcher into the boot you turn a screw handle to expand the stretcher  this handle turns very easily even when the boot starts getting tight so keep your eyes on the boot and dont start out with too much pressure  it seemed to me that it might have been possible to split the boot with less effort than one would imagine but this was just my impression  highly recommend this for tweaking the fit of any boots that arent quite wide enough

review: excellent sun hat for sunny days  it provides great protection from the sun for the face ears and neck  my son loves wearing it  we get lots of compliments on it  it dries quickly so it is great to wear to the pool as well  the only disadvantage is that the brim of the hat is a bit floppy  otherwise it is an excellent buy
product: i play baby boys flap sun protection hat aqua wavy boats

review: i ordered the set and it got here within  days so i was really happy with the shipping after reading the other review i was a little worried but after the bracelets arrived and i could see them myself i was pleased with them to me they didnt look cheap at all they looked just like the picture showed which is what i wanted in the first place
product: brown braided leather bracelet w metal anchor  sailor wheel design in blue leather string

review: these were recommended by a family member who owns a shoe store  i could have ordered them from her but it would have taken a week or so but got these from amazon rather quickly  they provide solid support in my work boots and help my feet to not be sore at the end of the day  i will definitely be ordering again
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: our toddler loves all things penguin so we decided that for his birthday party wed have a penguinpalooza in june when i found this onesie allowing him to become a penguin i clicked buy now and only felt a little silly when the onesie arrived i will admit to being a bit surprisedthe safaritype box looks a lot bigger on amazon than in real lifebut the onesie itself looked great weve washed it three times now once before wearing and since hes already worn it twice in the last week two more times and the quality looks great the material of the onesie is very soft the color is vibrant and the facts on the back are great a fun find and definitely an impulse buy that im glad to have made
product: peekazoo unisex baby infant become an animal short sleeve onesie bodysuit

review: fits perfectly just what i was looking for i have  cards and about  bills in the money clip i am able to push the cards up and then fan them out to pick the card i want fits easily in my front pocket should have done this years ago
product: carbon fiber money clip walletcl carbonlife business card holder rfid protector credit card holder wallet clips for men

review: i bought the same exact mitten in orange last year for my  year old daughter it was perfect she wore it nicely and was able to move her hand comfortable wearing it and its super soft which is why i ordered a second pair this year as a backup the reason i gave it  stars is bcd this green mittens strings turned out to be very small huge difference from the orange one its the same exact brand i dont understand why the makers decided to shorten the string my daughter was was able to put her hands in them but couldnt move them anymore so she is still wearing the orange ones from last year  i m a disappointed i hope they fix this issue
product: zutano baby fleece mittens

review: the size chart helps out a lot im normally a size  junior size and the medium fit me perfect length is good too im  just fyi the strings will pull easily i would recommend you keep in the bag it comes with also being gentle when putting it on and off
product: california costumes fashion flapper adult costume

review: my old stainless steel money clip mc broke and was not repairable  looked all over for replacement but very few that would accept more than a few cards or bills  bought this serman brands mc and it was just what i was looking for  it is lightweight has a  inch gap when fully open  i regularly carry  credit cards or hotelstore cards and  bills  the mc has been in use now for about  months and has not lost any of its holding power so all the cards and bills are tightly held but still accessible  so much nicer than a billfold
product: serman brands carbon fiber money clip credit card holder slim business card holder clips for men glossy

review: very good foot support at a great price  i have worn dr scholls custom  as well as prescription   i experience foot pain often especially if i am standing on concrete for any length of time  good orthotics in sturdy footwear helps a lot  i could not wear athletic shoes for more than about  minutes without my feet aching until i put a pair of these orthotics in my new balance shoes  i will buy more
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: this is probably the  wig ive bought from amazon most cheaper some more expensive this is by far the cheapest looking one ive gotten i wear wigs to work frequently and i dont mind looking like im wearing a wig but not like one i bought at a halloween store most people who dont know me dont realize im wearing wigspros the color the blue is exactly how it looks on my monitor its hard to find a long blue wig that isnt dark blue or a very bright lighter blue if this had been any other color i would have returned itcons the fit is weird and lumpy its the first wig that has fit me this way so id say i have an average head using the snaps didnt help and in fact if anything made the lumps more pronounced it is a full wig at the bottom but the top is very thin ive never had a wig before where you could see the weftsbase of the wig before it would have helped if the base wasnt such a lightpeachy color which is also problematic at the front hairlineif youre wearing a hat over it the lumpiness and thin top wont be apparent but i tried that and my hat kept sliding off ill keep searching for a decent blue wig
product: newpeck girls fashion wavy curly long hair women party cosplay wig gray blue color

review: this is our favorite baby sun hatthe striped pattern is charming and we get loads of compliments the fit is as expected my tiny baby has normal sized head and weve been rocking this hat from about  months until  months when we just lost it on vacation the feature that helps the fit is the under chin strings that tie into a bow so you can customize the fit most of our other hats have a velcro strip or button snap so we cant get the hat snuggerthe brim is wide enough to keep her eyes and face shaded but not too big since we often babywear with an ergo carrier we find some other hats that are really wide brimmed get turned around or pulled down by the carrier and baby gets annoyed this hat is just rightwe are cheapos and we felt like this hat was worth it we bought the hat in  and the same one again in  even after losing our bigger one i will purchase the hat again to replace it thats rare for our family where we mostly have hand me downs and sale stuff from bargain stores
product: zutano baby upf  sun protection hat

review: very good color and material was very sturdy and well made would recommend though i will say since i am a female with an average neck even when i tightened this as tight as i could get it the tie still was a bit loose on my neck not enough to make it unwearable though
product: mens rainbow pride striped formal pretied bow tie neckwear

review: when the glasses were delivered they were delivered underneath the welcome mat at the entry of my house the glasses were underneath the mat i was not aware of this and people walked over them for a couple of days now my daughter wears all bent glasses all bent out of shape
product: caixia unisex  thin metal frame engraved detail round  eyeglasses

review: these are a stylish looking pair of shades fit my  year old son perfectly i was hesitant to purchase due to it being listed as ages  i couldnt imagine how one pair of sunglasses was to fit all ages  but figured for the price what the heck right figured if it didnt fit i could return them or gift them to another childthey fit nicely not to loose or tight my son wore them for hours while playing in the ocean and while building sand castles they didnt slide or fall off he didnt complain about them being too tight or uncomfortablei loved that they are a soft plastic frame i dropped them on the ceramic tiles in our kitchen and they didnt break honestly not even a scratch which as a parent this is important to me they also came with a soft carrying case that doubles as an eye glass cleaner toohes had them approximately  days now and they arent broken scratched or destroyed definitely a nice purchase at a killer pricefyi i tried them on my  year old daughter yeah no they dont fit the sizing should probably be  in my opinion
product: kids comfortable classic sunglasses for boys and girls  toddler preschool grade school children age  years recommended

review: there is a information problem in general for the size of this insert  i had to cut it in half to make it work  now i have two the inserts are getting a little beat up already  the fix would be for me to get the wallet that these inserts were made for  otherwise the product was shipped promptly
product: plastic wallet inserts replacement windows d credit card

review: i just got these today i have been having pain in both feet when walking for a month or two nothing seemed to help i tried pain relieving creams and epsom salt none of these worked but these socks seem to ease the pain they are very comfortable and i have had them on for about  hours now i will be buying more of these i will wear these regularly and will try to leave another review soon also these socks came faster than the estimated time which was supposed to be the middle of next month they also came packaged very nicely
product: tasom toe alignment socks  toe gel socks  toes spreaders spacer  separator

review: these are my favorite i live in the south and i bought these as replacements for a pair i had worn constantly for at least  years flip flop weather can be at any time of year here so they are definitely go to shoes best made and so very comfortable
product: havaianas womens top flip flop sandal

review: i tried to put these on with my earrings on not large at all and they wouldnt attach i would get them around my ears and click them to attach and they wouldnt grab my ears at all after i took my earrings off they did attach but not securely at all they certainly do not hug my ears like i would want them to do i will be returning them
product: ear mitts bandless ear muffs for men  women soft fleece ear warmers  sizes

review: i bought this watch to have on hand when it is not convenient to wear a watch  it is easy to read without glasses but it is a cheap watch  the design came off of the cover but it works great  so far its keeping good time
product: yesurprise ceramic painting style necklace pocket chain pendant quartz watch  flower blue

review: so much fun to see our   year old grandson in his one piece fuzzy pjs run around with this huge helmet  he certainly looked like an alien from the  and   he loved it even if he could not quite reach the buttons  it is sized for a larger child ages  but with help we managed  there is not a lot of rocketship stuff for that age so ordered it knowing it would probably be too big appears to be solidly constructed  i appreciate the volume of the countdown  it is not too loud
product: aeromax jr astronaut helmet with sounds

review: not a bad pair of leggings the patterndesign is as pictured and pretty cool the fabric is ok not super smooth and soft but not horrible  i believe its more polyester and less cotton  the fit was a tad weird for me as i am hippy so it fit a bit weird at the hips and rested at the lowest part of my hips which is fine when im standing but not so great if i squat or bend over  the pattern gets a tad see thru the more it has to stretch so be careful when under garmets you choose to wear underneath  overal it was slightly more snug though the thights and calf than i care for so i gave them to my daughter
product: chocolate pickle womens plus skull rose print stretch leggings

review: one of the most comfortable shirts i own did not shrink after washing very breathable and i own many ua shirts and this is more comfortable at a fraction of the cost even the white can be worn as a under shirt or on its own i love it in this az weather
product: bellacanvas mens triblend tee  white fleck triblend  s

review: its a rain jacket so it does what its supposed to do it keeps you dry i originally bought it for a trip to yellowstone to roll up in my hiking backpack in case of rain but i used it multiple times before the trip and was pleasantly surprised by how dry and warm i stayed when wearing it went out fourwheeling in a storm in montana in  weather wearing this and my upper half was bone dry and i stayed decently warm its too large for me ordered xs  and  lbs so if youre inbetween sizes definitely size down overall its a good rain jacket for the price columbia youve done it again
product: columbia womens arcadia ii waterproof rain jacket

review: the clarity and antiglare are great  a little heavy but seem more durable because of it  i dont really like the style its too masculine but ill take great vision over style for driving glasses any day  so pleased i bought  more pair  at  a pair this is a great deal on a very good product

review: this is a decent hat and im torn about the review some aspects are great others are very lacking lets start with my head size i wear a      fitted caps bigger noggin but not enormous in regards to the hat the black fabric under the rim really helps reduce glare i used the hat at beaches and many pool decks and can attest to this but it only comes in one size and that one size is a bit too small for my head i realize my large dome is my problem and this hats fits most people well or even a bit too big but the rim of the hat sits funny got oddly molded in the box it was shipped it which was too small for the hat and its never really recovered to normal the bill has always had this weird ridge in it right where it meets the top part of the hat and it sits unevenly ive been battling with the bill of this hat since day one to try and get it to sit normal in a nice disc shape but the strap is nice the padding on the inside of the hat that goes around your dome to prevent scratchy straw on your skin is also a nice touch if you have a big dome or like your straw hats to sit nicely and not warp and get bent out of shape you may want to try buying a handmade hat from someone at a local farmers marketat least thats what i had to doupdate after about  years this hat started to break down considerably should be noted that it did get worn about  a month and bumped around occasionally in the house with the hats but nothing abnormal its a straw hat so some of the breakdown was expected and none of the holes prevented it from being used properly unless you have a bald head in which case it could cause a weird sunburnluckily my hair is long but the woven hat material became very fragile after a year or so and started easily breaking off from touching almost anything after about  yearsgood luck

review: lets be honest your looking to buy this product to do one of the following give your body a nice shape try to flatten your tummy shed a few inches off your waist or even posture hell maybe even all of them  im here to honestly tell you how your experience will be with this cincherplease remember cinchers are different than corsets corsets are made for more serious waist trainingposture i have been using this product for about a week and a half and with it on notice a change in my posture mostly because with it on it is uncomfortable to really slouch uncomfortable not unbearable you most likely sit straighter because the bones in it are plastic and you might break them doing some dramatic moves ive noticed i walk taller and sit straighter with it onsizing based on other reviews im sure you notice there is a lot of issues when it comes to choosing the correct size due to the inconsistency im going to try my best to make this as simple as possible i am a  bra size when wearing womens tshirts i am a medium mens small and in dresses i am most comfortable in an  the reviews told me to order  sizes up so i did buying  an extralarge xlhow it fit the first time i ever used the cincher i was able to put it on the tightest setting second row ideally you want to first be able to put it on the loosest setting  row then graduate to the second you know its working and that your waist may be getting smaller i may have been better off getting a large i have ordered another cincher and this time a large as far as the initial size i bought xl its not too tight even on the second setting  when i say not too tight i mean that i can breathe in it  i do feel compression and it does flatten me out but id rather have a large just for my preference so keep that in mind i will say that the xl for me starting off on the second setting was probably a good starting point seeing as though i never typically wear cinchers or corsetsgym use so far i have used this cincher in the gym it was not uncomfortable even when sitting down and doing floor exercises it does give compression allowing for proper use and that little extra something to work your abs  in comparison to a typical exercise bandits does not collect a lot of sweat so its not extra gross when taking it off after a workoutbody shaping okay im sure this is where many of you jumped down to trust me this was all i was searching for in reviews so this cincher actually does give the appearance of a flatter tummy and smaller waist under my clothes but it is not a dramatic difference i bought this to introduce my tummy and waist to the idea of waist training  if these are your intentions this product is a good place to start however if you are seeking a product to begin serious waist training it is best to begin with a steel boned corset this cincher easily takes away  inches of your waist may be another inch or two more but i would need a smaller size to be sure does give a more flattering appearance under your clothes and active wear at the gym body results like i have stated previously i have only had the product after a week in a half so far i have seen a slight difference im not sure if its just when i take it off because everything still seems to be sitting in the right place but i do feel like im pinching less when touching poking and my sides the current results make me optimistic about future results so i will keep usingflaws i can see the cincher hooks through my clothes i would not recommend wearing with skin tight apparel if you bend the bones they will snap since i have a relatively short torso this cincher meets my bra sometimes pushing in my underwire which is sometimes uncomfortablewelp thats pretty much all i have if you have any additional comments or questions feel free to contact me at    i am not paid or anything i just know how hard it is to find honest thorough reviews i am not sure if amazon has a messaging center but if they do you can message me there as well happy cinching

review: havaianas are my favorite flip flop i have had knee surgery in the past and can feel confident when wearing these shoes around water i would recommend this brand to anyone who has ever slipped while wearing flip flops you will not fall the worst thats happened to me was walking out of the shoe because it was firmly gripped to the wet surface i was walking across
product: havaianas womens top flip flop sandal

review: i got this ring for my mom for christmas since i was on a budget and had a lot of people to shop for it was perfectly priced and when it arrivedit was absolutely stunning the color of the green amethyst was pale but i was expecting that i love the vintage look it carries and it is soooo sparkly i highly recommend this ring to anyone looking for a classy beautiful piece
product: sterling silver green amethyst ring

review: the ring arrived on time which is nice it is a very nice design my husband of  years never wore his weeding band so i figured if i got him a camo one that may change because he is all about hunting  he likes the ring but cannot wear it for long periods of time because it is so thick that it irritates his fingers next to it
product: camo wedding rings by  camo  camo engagement rings  flat titanium

review: i love these bracelets my first one served me for well over a year of day to day wear and tear until my ex ended up keeping it when we split but these little bracelets are perfect for anyone who wants so show their pride without something too flashy great product the magnet is strong enough that i have never had problems with it coming off
product: nanafast titanium stainless steel magnet rainbow lgbt pride handmade braided bracelet pu leather weave plaited jewelry

review: i often buy these locally but have become somewhat disappointed with both the increased price and lack of availability  i was very pleased to see they were offered through amazon so i gave it a try and glad i did the are the same quality at a better price
product: assets by sara blakely midthigh shaper super control

review: i was so excited to get these labels and used them on my childs shoes and boots right away i followed the instructions but the labels started moving around in the shoes on the very first day the labels were also very easy to come off i actually had better luck in the past using the avery noiron clothes labels when in a pinch for a solution to label shoes on their inside
product: children shoe labels  self laminating

review: ive purchased this brand before and these are smaller than the other styles i got last year i am going to have to order up a sizei ordered a size up and while there is plenty of room in the length theyre a bit long the real issue is that the straps bubble away from my foot i have high arches so this is rarely a problem theyre cute shoes and i wish i could have made them work i ordered the cream of the style i purchased last year
product: funtasma womens  slide pump

review: loving this card holder so far i have  cards in it and it will have some room for a few bills it feels fairly durable with a nice finishbut ive only been using for a few weeks so ill update after a few months the only reason i didnt give it  stars is i wish it could hold at least a few more cardsbillsif you put too much inside it will open and wont stay shut maybe make a unit slightly larger for those of us with more cards
product: best rfid blocking card holder case for men and women slim stainless steel metal wallet

review: i had been looking for a wristlet that was slim enough to fit in a laptop bag but also held my phone  this is awesome  it is the perfect size and expands when i need it to  it actually holds the  phones i sometimes carry for work  there are  zipper pockets which are perfect for change and then a spot for other stuff like lipstick or something  the leather is great and color was true to the picture
product: befen women leather zipper phone wallet with card holdercash pocketwrist strap

product: volcom mens frickin modern stretch chino short

review: there are few things less adorable than a toddler wearing suspenders this being said my son was only able to wear these for a month before the clasps stopped holding on to his pants no matter how loose i made these they would not stay attached i finally threw them away since they were causing him such frustration if you are looking for something cute for an event or picture where your child is only going to wear them once maybe twice you really cant beat the price but these are not for everyday wearplay
product: buyless fashion suspenders for kids and baby adjustable elastic solid color  inch

review: i really like the design and color of this rolling cart i would have given it a  star review if the wheels were stronger  however the tiny plastic wheels are worn already and i only used it once outside  the wheels are made for indoor use only  my husband is going to try to replace the wheels with ball bearing rubber wheels which are much stronger softer and wont crack like the plastic wheels  i would have paid more for this tote if it had the ball bearing wheels  if you want to use this tote on outside sidewalks then i dont recommend it unless you want to spend time and money replacing the wheels  the size is just right  i bought this so that i could take this to the mall when im shopping and carrying some heavy items or lots of bags  if you have back problems or other medical restrictions for carrying or lifting heaving objects then a rolling tote is ideal
product: goodhope rolling dual handle shopper tote black

review: similar to other reviewers i have had a hard time finding warm gloves that fit my  well she attends outdoor preschool so she needs layers to stay warm in the elementspluses the price is right about  these gloves are warm fit her hands well and fit inside her waterproof abecko mittensminuses they arent windproof the wide knit lets cold air in they have loose threads and leave fluff all over the place i bet they dont last long we were also sent duplicate colors instead of the six unique patterns advertised
product: toddler soft and warm fleece lined gloves  fuzzy gloves

review: its well made but expensive for what it is  i was   prepregnancy and the smallest sized fit well around my waist but unzipped jeans looked a little lumpy underneath this material so i never ended up using it after trying it on a couple of timesi resorted to using the rubber band trick  and wearing long tight spandexy tank tops under my clothes to cover the zipperive attached a ton of pictures to give you a sense of what it looks like out of the boxit comes with a cute free magnet that says yes you look beautiful thats still on my fridge and has gotten way more mileage than the belly band itself
product: ingrid  isabel womens maternity everyday bellaband

review: chose  the wine frame with brown lens as i didnt want  a dark lens  they look and fit very good  they came with a tightening tool a cloth for cleaning a hard case and a soft cloth holder  im impressed with this company with the quality and the packaging
product: duco semi rimless sunglasses for prescription eyewear polarized sunglasses

review: super cute nice and flexible with good traction and easy on and off size was right on and my  yr old son says they are comfortable we have only worn them  times so far so i cant say how the quality is yet so far so good i would recommend these boots
product: oaki kids rubber rain boots with easyon handles for children  toddlers

review: rather than three pairs of uniform  plugs i received onyx and amythyst plugs that are both  and true to size but the amythyst flair is much larger than the onyx the white jade is lovely but is  i saw that other customers have received a similar grab bag of items if these had been uniform as pictured i would have given them  stars hands down
product: set of  pairs single flare stone plugs      white jade amethyst black agate

review: was disappointed in the length of this romper  it is quite short comparing it to other rompers i have purchased in the past  my daughter was  months old and she is petite  if you child is average height i would recommend the next size up  the shirt is cheap fabric  it looks very stretched out just from one wash  its cute but not that well made
product: rene rofe baby girls  piece corduroy jumper set with lap shoulder longsleeve bodysuit infant

review: i have permanently switched from traditional belts with holes to ratchet belts  the buckle is heavy well made and the entire item appears durable for the fraction of the price of boutique ratchet belts  moreover i get the custom fit i want cutting the belt down to the perfect size  even if after the first trim the belt is still a bit big it isnt much trouble to remove the buckle and trim a bit more  just do not err and cut too much  overall very pleased with my purchase and get compliments on my new belt weather wearing as a casual belt or at work in a professional setting
product: marino avenue mens genuine leather ratchet dress belt with linxx buckle enclosed in an elegant gift box

review: great running pack so long as you keep it light weight the back mesh is great for your phone since it is closer to your body offering a better center of gravity as your phone is most likely the heaviest my leather wallet with about  plastic cards and a few bills fit snug in the front rfid protected zippered pocket seams are well made and do not appear to have any issues adjustment is held together with a buckled nylon strap ive had experiences with an elastic type pack which couldnt handle the weight of a full sized smartphone highly recommended and a great product
product: rfid blocking waist wallet  money belt  travel belt  passport holder  card wallet

review: love it matches my wristlet didnt understand for sure why it was called doubleeye but that is because it can hold  pair of glasses if necessary  both being right there in front separated by the padded material i only need it for  pair of reading glasses but seems like it would work fine with two pairs of glasses
product: vera bradley double eye ink blue

review: ordered one and it broke  weeks later but  the owner actually emailed me and sent me another one  thought that was awesome  new one looks great hopefully it doesnt break but only time will tell they feel real but im not a gem genius gem genius  lol  sure  so they could be fake  meh theyre gorgeous so i dont care
product: jewelrieshop unisex synthetic stones healing power crystal elastic stretch  bead bracelet bangle

review: we used this all summer at the beach and every mess was contained  cleanup wasnt an issue since we just added it to our regular load of cloth diapers  it held onto sand no matter how many times we rinsed and washed itit got trapped between the layers somehow  my daughter wore a large at  pounds and this one may not fit her by the winter  ill get the next size up though because we were happy with the overall performance and the ruffles on it are adorable

review: i have a child in  and another in  and i let them both pick out their backpacks online  apparently i have some good shoppers on my hands as im happy with their selection the designs are really cute and funadditionally these backpacks are nice and sturdy and the perfect size for a little one  we used quilted backpacks last year and they showed dirt easily and werent firm enough for folders and paperwork  everything was a crumpled mess by the time they came home  however these are just the right size  they arent too big as some tend to be for a preschoolerkindergartner  but they are big enough to hold folderspapers and leave a little extra room  i read some reviews that question their longevity  we are only  weeks into school so i cant speak to that  the price is reasonable too  overall good product
product: stephen joseph little girls  little girls  gogo bag flower one size

review: i am a little disappointed with the design it has a lot of pockets but the cell phone pocket is very small and can only hold a small flip phone the thing i am most disappointed with is the quality the stitching on the strap was coming off in several places when it arrived
product: goson cowhid leather handbag purse with cell phone holder  many pocket

review: just started potty training our two year old and he loves sesame street so i thought these would be a great tool to help out i was right he loves the characters and the bright colors elmo big bird oscar and super groverhis favorite by the way the size is  but they seem a little small they are also a little stiff probably due to all the graphics on them for the exception of those two items i wouldve given  stars
product: sesame street boys toddler

review: im not a big ringwearer so for my weddingengagement ring i wanted something lowprofile scratchresistant and comfortable i couldnt have done any better than this ring especially for such an unbeatable price ive been wearing it more than a year now and the only thing that has been able to scratch it was an impressive bike crash that sent me scraping along the asphalt and even after that the scratches are nearly invisible ive also managed to drop it plenty of times with no problems id definitely recommend it
product: mj metals jewelry  to  white tungsten carbide mirror polished classic wedding ring

review: used these gloves recently in ny city during a very frosty time they kept my hands warmer than my leather gloves and i could access my phone without removing my gloves also the price is right as i lost one reordered and received the new pair in less time than the arrival dates was noted on the purchase email
product: iglove unisex touch screen knit glove hand warm for iphone ipad blackberry samsung htc and other smartphones pda one size

review: so i have no negative feelings about this product despite having returned it i will however say that its pretty tough to have issues with a product thats literally a piece of nylon and six pieces of metal it looks like the pictureso if you like what the picture looks like and like  ring nato bands this is a good product
product: clockwork synergy   ring heavy nato pvd black watch strap bands

review: this tote is made of very strong materials excellent for passing security check points and the small pocket on the insideis perfect for keeping things that would get lost on the bottom  the only negative is that the ends of the zippered top arenot sealed against weather  still a great purchase
product: clear stadium bag clear tote bag nfl stadium approved  x  x  with adjustable shoulder strap and handles

review: do not buy a new style of pointe shoes off the internet  i was fitted into the rubin at an actual store and used amazon to buy a new pair after those wore out  overall these are a good product and they helped me focus on my technique rather than worrying about my shoes and my feet  but pointe shoes are such a personal item that even though i had a good experience with them its totally irrelevant whether or not someone else will be responsible and get fitted for your pointes
product: russian pointe rubin pointe shoes ucut flexible medium shank

review: this item looked like the perfect replacement for my worn out double wide card holder all reviews were good wellno longer i have two problems that make this item unusable for me the height dimension is just a hair bigger than my old insert this means the new one extends a bit above andor below the wallet dimension  and the reason for this extra height is that the cards insert from the top rather than from the inside protected end of the card sleeves this means that if you drop the wallet the upper stack of cards could easily come shooting out nothing to stop themnot a good design in my opinion
product: plastic wallet inserts replacement windows d credit card

review: i absolutely love this sweater but i shouldve ordered a small intead of a medium washes  dries beautifully as yes i did dry it on high to try to shrink it on me its a cowl neck instead of off the shoulders  its so long i wear it with skinny jeans or leggings it still works  i love it so much i ordered one in tan in a small i weigh  lbs  wear a  c
product: merryfun womens spring offshoulder pullover sweater bottoming shirt

review: the bottle of joules buffer up rain boot gloss spray was delivered in a plasticlined envelope without a cap  the package was a mess since a lot of the liquid was outside the bottle  after handling the bottle with product all over it i realized the label advises not getting it on skin  greeeaaaaaaaat
product: joules womens buffer up

review: these love heart shield bar nipple rings made out of steel are so very very sexy that my husband could not take his eyes off of my breasts they sure make me feel sexy especially when i am wearing them underneath my outfit  i loves these and i really would like to find a pair that are similar
product: steel love heart nipple shield bar ring body piercing jewelry

review: i ordered this because i wanted a hat with a tie so the wind wouldnt blow it off  it works great  the cap part adjusts to the best fitting size and the brim is big enough it even covers my daughters shoulders which is great for her fair skin
product: i play girls baby brim sun protection hat aqua shellflowers

review: this bracelet is adorable i love the two tone bronze and silver color that matches almost any other jewelry  i was happily surprised that the ovals have words on both sides so you can spin them to get the words that inspire you  i like to choose an intention each day and put those words on top so i am reminded of them throughout the day  the quality of the beads and ovals is good and it is on a stretch string so it will fit almost everybody  overall it very cute and i am very happy with it  this product was provided at a discounted price in exchange for my honest review

review: i dont normally take the time to write reviews but i find them useful when im making purchases so thought it the right thing to do  i concur with most of the other reviews on this product  its excellent quality especially for the price ive been wearing mine with a pendant attached for a week now with no issues  the plating seems very durable my pendant is a pretty serious fossilized shark tooth and it hasnt rubbed the plating off yet  im very sensitive to alloys  so far the only metals ive been able to wear without a rash are  or higher grade gold tungsten and surgical stainless  my skin hasnt reacted to this chain whatsoever  the clasp seems very sturdy and the spring in the lobster claw seems stout enough to withstand the test of time
product: besteel jewelry  mens womens stainless steel wheat chain necklace link black  inch

review: i dont think ive ever left a product review but i have to on this onei am an insurance adjuster which has me doing lots of dirty work most often i am on ladders and on roofs and scrambling around shingles i have been doing this job for about  months and it has absolutely killed my beautiful engagement ringafter lots of googling i found this product and figured i would give it a tryit fits comfortably and protects every part of my ring i love that there are  in here so i can keep them in various spots its amazing that it protects not only the bottom of the ring but the stone as wellthis product is incredible for any woman who has to do some dirty work but wants to protect a precious ringi wish there were more women in my field so i could rave about this product some more
product: carering cover silicone ring protector for womens rings

review: very beautiful simple looking fan has a very spanish look to it which is why i ordered it so i can use it from my fan dancing the fan slides very easily open to close i would recommend it to anyone and i will order from these people any time because they quickly shipped everything
product: amico black plastic frame embroidery floral detail folding hand fan

review: so i have extremely high arches and i also have runners knee i overpronate too i bought brooks sneakers and my runners knee pain almost fully stopped immediately but i still had some issues with stiffness discomfort and cracking in my knees i was feeling like if i had extra arch support that would help so i looked around and found these and since they help with pronation as well i decided to try them they took some time to get used to they have a harder shell under the arch and heel i could feel them under my arches which surprised me as nothing is ever high enough to fill in all the negative space between my arch and the shoe at first i wished it was softer because i was nervous my arches would get sore from the hard shell i was pleasantly surprised that after the first use i had zero cracking or tension in my knees i took them out for an hour because i was bothered by the arch support a bit and felt a little sore but almost immediately my knee started cracking again so i put them back in and it stopped by the end of the first day my arches had gotten used to the feeling and i was really happy and i have been using them everyday since the combination of the brooks sneakers and the pinnacle breeze insoles have alleviated all of my runners knee symptoms i have ordered a second pair to keep in my other shoes i bought the  womens and they fit perfectly in my shoes very satisfied and highly recommend for very high arches
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: i got three of these for  cartilage piercings in my ears they came in separate sealed bags which gave me confidence in their cleanliness i dont know if they have been autoclaved but my piercings are old and well healed so i wasnt worried about that i am happy with the coloring of the rose gold plating as well as the appearance of the opal im pretty sure the opal like bead on the captive is plastic but it looks nice so far i am very happy with them and  would order them again my only complaint is that this jewelry dropped  in price right after i purchased it this is good news for you future buyers but a bummer for me
product: pierced owl opal captive bead ring   surgical steel

review: its a really pretty ring ive looked at quite a few  stone rings and i really like the shape of this one the stones stick out more instead of set into the ring itself im not sure how it will hold up because i just got it it does look like the real one the color of stones i will have to say tho im not real keen on the bow shape holding the stones on sides thats just a taste preference tho

review: these headbands came quickly and were exactly as describedthey are super adorable they have quite a bit of stretchinessversatility as well as they fit my  month olds head and my  and  year olds heads as well they are easy to put on and my  month old leaves these on longer than the typical  seconds that some other headbands last they do not leave any type of mark or indentations on her head either as some other headbands tend to dothe designs are also very cute and versatile i am able to pair them with many outfits that she already has i have already received several compliments on these headbands and have only taken her out wearing two different prints so i anticipate more to comeas a daily online buyer i know how important it is for reviews to be honest and unbiased i always spend time using a product before reviewing it typically  days at least i know how much reviews make an impact as to whether or not i purchase a product so i make sure that i take time and am very honest in hopes of helping others make an informed decision about said product the opinions expressed within this review are entirely my own with that being said i received this product either for  free or discounted in exchange for trying it out and giving an honest and unbiased review the sellers just want to know what every day ordinary people think of their product if this review was helpful please vote below

review: these fleece pajamas are a perfect fit i am  pounds a little over  feet tall and wear a small someone who gets cold easy loves to lounge and needs another reason to jump into your pajamas as soon as you get home from school or work you will want to buy another after you them in the mail these pajamamania pants were the perfect christmas gift and i would encourage others to also give as gifts they are warm enough on the coldest nights although they can sometimes get a little too warm they are my go to pajamascomfort made from plush fleece drawstring waistband pocketsbesides being so soft and made from plush fleece these pants are super comfortable and you will have a hard time getting out of bed in the morning knowing you have to take them off the drawstring waistband and pockets are the final touch that make these pants perfect you cannot compete with pajamas that have pocketsdurability doesnt shrink doesnt pillthese pajamamania pants hold up many times run through both the washer and dryer yes you can dry them and they dont shrink the biggest positive is that the fleece doesnt pill i end up giving away my clothes that pill because they are no longer comfortable you wont have to give these away they are great for someone that is looking for warm light breathable fit just right and even the perfect gift pajamaswhenever i am looking for more pajamas or an easy gift i know just were to go pajamamania perfect for both men and women i hope you love this product just as i do
product: pajamamania womens sleepwear fleece pajamas pj pants

review: i have been wearing powerstep pinnacle insoles for many years on the advice of my podiatrist because of a bad bout with plantar fasciitis i was very unhappy with the fact that their quality control had gone downhill and the company would do nothing about it nor would they stand behind their warrantywhen i saw the vienzone insoles advertised i decided to give them a try and boy am i happy i did they are far superior to powersteps at about half of the cost and have all the comfort if not more i will have to wear them and see how they hold up in the long run but i can say if they only last as long as the powersteps they will be worth the replacement cost the height and placement of the arch support is perfect for my foot and the  size is perfect with no trimming needed i bought multiple pairs so i can have them in all my shoes without having to switch
product: powerstep pinnacle orthotic shoe insoles

review: i wear a  at torrid and ordered the plus size  stockings when they arrived the package said suitable for  lbs that is not   the average  woman is a size  but i carried on anywaythe stockings stretched ok but there is no way that they would stay up without a garter belt they rolled down to my knees immediately with a garter belt the edges still rolled heavily so you dont get that smooth line like the picture there is no grippy texture on the thigh they are literally just hose piecesthey are also nonbreathable nylon not like regular pantyhose you get no air inside the hose my legs were sweaty and all the sweat just stayed in the hose with me grossall in all they are ok for light novelty wear but not allnight costume quality

review: it was very comfortable especially for the first days when youre not yet ready to wear something tight im a size  and bought a size s however as i recovered i wanted something tighter that helped more with the shaping so i turned to other products that were better suited for that

review: this coverall is super soft and stretchy  i ordered the  month and my  month   baby fits them well  i cuff up the legs because shes not tall enough for this size but because its so stretchy i ordered up and she can get a few months use out of them  she is wearing  month cotton sleepers for reference but seems to be outgrowing stuff quickly  i hope to use these coveralls for a handful of months as they seem to stretch quite a lot  i love the flap on the back to check diapers without having to unzip and pull a let out  worth the price

review: although it arrived later than expected it was worth it it is a bit pricey when compared to other options but i have always been a lover of the celtic designs leather and the color green so obviously this stood out to me the fact that it was handmade is what sold me im a sucker for items handmade im am simply blown away by the quality and craftsmanship that went into this cover it is very substantial in its thickness and feel but not at all bulky the pictures simply do no justice to the product and i highly recommend it to those who are interested i will definitely be returning to purchase more accessories from this vendor i look forward to my many years of use

review: nicely made but not sure if it is sterling silver it looks like it might tarnish easily well crafted but the copper wiring is very prevalent it looks different but the energy from it seems good i havent measured with an emf detector but i have it next to my bed and sleep more peacefully i would like to think its helping my energy etc who knows though until you can measure it for now ill keep it but wish i could have seen from the picture that the copper wire shows so much more than the turquoise hope this helps buying on line is tricky
product: orgone energy reversible pendant necklace in antique silver finish with turquoise  leather

review: im not sure why these hats have rave reviews all the other sun hats we have use velcro to close under the chin which is much easier to manage with a squirmy babytoddler than having to tie strings together plus the velcro could break open in some kind of strangulation situation where a knot would stay in place also this hat is machine washable but cannot go in the dryer ive washed it a couple times and it comes out covered in lint i washed it with regular clothes not towels or anything linty it constantly falls down in front of my sons eyes so he cant see overall i was really disappointed with this hat i had high expectations based on other reviews i wouldnt buy another one there are better options

review: ive never been a fan of purses and this was an awesome alternative it has enough space for several cards i currently have  in mine and easily fits in the comically small pockets on womens pants i could definitely fit more cards in if i wanted to but the wallet starts to accordion at that pointsive had mine for several months now and its holding up really well except for the green strap i think all of the stretching putting things into and getting things out of the wallet has been wearing out the elastic of the green band a little but its still pretty much perfect and i would buy this wallet again if i needed to

review: an absolutely great product genuine leather well constructed and beautifully designed i had been looking for something that i could easily carry my phone and my immediate necessities in it even has a small change pocket inside which for me was a pleasant surprise i ordered the grey one and the black one and will be ordering the saddle colored one i use it as my only wallet in my tote but can fit it in my smaller purse as well not worried about leaving it because it can stay on my wrist i didnt use the extra fancy tassel but it came included so if ever i choose to switch it up i can my iphone  slides in smoothly to the slit made for it and i dont have to wrestle with the wristlet when i try to remove it  you wont regret this purchase definitely a must buy

review: i ordered two of these so i could mimic the style shown in the picture one of them came broken i suspect it was packaged broken because one link had fallen off but there was only one circle connector in the bag instead of the two needed to put it back on it should be an easy fix but it shouldnt have to be fixed also it twists easily so im not sure that it will hold up wellthe reason i still decided to give it a  is because although i was underwhelmed when i took it out of the bag once i put it in my hair i loved it it is very elegant with just enough sparkle to catch the eye it also manages to be exactly the right size for my head im able to do some really lovely headband styles ive been wanting to do but other bands are too big or too small to work well obviously thats a pretty personal thing but the other nice thing is that if its too big for your head its easy to remove a linkif it holds up this will definitely be one of my favoriteshopefully they will replace the broken one ill update here if they make that hard otherwise you can assume they were on top of it still very frustrating given how long it has to take to ship in the first place

review: i ordered  after having my first child and i dont feel like it helped at all in shrinking my belly i follow the sizing guidelines and it fit fine ill admit it was a good support garment because you basically have no core after childbirth and it is probably really beneficial if you have a c section i didnt i was fortunate not have much of a belly after he was born in fact i think i have more of one now and im not sure if it is because i didnt wear my belky bandit for the recommended amount of time i was able to tolerate it for  weeks day and night not the  they say produces the best results it is stiff and does not move with your body it is difficult to wear under your clothes and does not stay in place it requires constant readjusting the worst was at night when it would slide up on my abdomen and squash my sore milkengorged boobs my biggest complaint is it is not machine washable and if anyone else is like me it would get soaked during my delightful postpartum hormone sweats not fun

review: i have been wearing them in my running shoes for over  years  i have slight pronation in both feet and these add the support i need to help with this problem  i run about  days a week or a total of about  miles  i buy new running shoes about once a year however others may prefer to buy shoes more often in this mileage category  when replacing my running shoes i look into the need to replace the orthotics as well but only do so if i dont like the way they are wearing  i have gotten more than  shoe change out of them  year but you need to be careful to inspect them at least annually due to the fact that once they decide to give out usually in the arch where the seam of hard plastic meets the softer front piece they go fast  i missed a small crack in the area outlined and about  miles into an  mile run the hard plastic broke through the soft padding and caused a nasty blister on my arch that took a long time to heal
